#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; is an easy to use personal information manager (<acronym>PIM</"
"acronym>). You can write journal entries, schedule appointments, events, and "
"to-dos. &korganizer; will remind you about pending tasks, and help you keep "
"your schedule."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; je enostaven za uporabo upravitelj osebnih podatkov "
"(<acronym>PIM</acronym>). Pišete lahko vnose v dnevnik, načrtujete sestanke, "
"dogodke in opravila &korganizer; vas bo spomnil na čakajoče naloge in vam "
"pomagal obdržati vaš časovni plan."

