#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; is an intuitive and easy to use personal information manager "
"(<abbrev>PIM</abbrev>). You can schedule appointments, events, create to-dos "
"and write journal entries. &korganizer; will remind you about pending tasks, "
"record your occurrences, experiences, and reflections and help you keep your "
"schedule."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; je intuitiven in enostaven za uporabo upravitelj osebnih "
"podatkov(<abbrev>PIM</abbrev>). Načrtujete lahko sestanke, dogodke, "
"ustvarite opravilain pišete vnose v dnevnik. &korganizer; vas bo spomnil na "
"čakajoče naloge,zabeleži svoje dogodke, izkušnje in razmišljanja ter vam "
"pomaga ohranjati svojčasovni plan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"But &korganizer; is not only about your personal calendar, it can help you "
"to interact with your colleagues and friends too. With &korganizer;, you can "
"invite anyone with an email address to an event and process responses, and "
"share a calendar (using a groupware server or simply a file over the "
"network). &korganizer; is based on open standards, and works with many "
"different group scheduling servers, giving you the control over your "
"information and the freedom to choose the best solutions."
msgstr ""
"Vendar &korganizer; ni namenjen le vašemu osebnemu koledarju, temveč vam "
"lahko pomaga tudi pri interakciji s sodelavci in prijatelji. Z &korganizer; "
"lahko na dogodek povabite kogar koli z e-poštnim naslovom in obdelate "
"odgovore ter delite koledar (z uporabo strežnika za skupinsko delo ali "
"preprosto datoteke prek omrežja). &korganizer; temelji na odprtih standardih "
"in deluje s številnimi različnimi strežniki za skupinsko planiranje, kar vam "
"daje nadzor nad vašimi podatki in svobodo izbire najboljših rešitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; is also the calendar, journal and to-do component of &kontact;, "
"offering you an integrated solution for your communication and information "
"management needs: email, notes, contacts management, news reader and news "
"feeds reader. Even if you do not use it inside &kontact;, &korganizer; is "
"integrated with the other &kde; <acronym>PIM</acronym> applications. For "
"instance, you can configure it to show birthdays from &kaddressbook; in your "
"agenda, use &kmail; to send and receive invitations, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; je tudi koledar, dnevnik in komponenta opravil &kontact;a, ki "
"vam ponuja integrirano rešitev za vašo komunikacijo in potrebe upravljanja "
"informacij: e-pošta, beležke, upravljanje stikov, bralnik novic in bralnik "
"virov novic. Tudi če ga ne uporabljate znotraj &kontact;, je &korganizer; "
"integriran z drugimi &kde; <acronym>PIM</acronym> aplikacijami. Na na "
"primer, lahko ga konfigurirate tako, da prikazuje rojstne dneve iz "
"&kaddressbook; v vašem dnevnem redu, uporabite &kmail; za pošiljanje in "
"prejemanje povabil, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main features of &korganizer;:"
msgstr "Glavne značilnosti &korganizer;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create To-dos, schedule events, and write journal entries."
msgstr "Ustvarite opravila, načrtujte dogodke in pišete vnose v dnevnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Organize your events and to-dos by grouping the related items with tags."
msgstr ""
"Organizirajte svoje dogodke in opravila tako, da združite povezane elemente "
"z oznakami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight tags with colors."
msgstr "Označite oznake z barvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open multiple calendars, and seamlessly view and edit them."
msgstr "Odprete več koledarjev ter si jih nemoteno ogledujete in urejate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reschedule your events by drag-and-drop."
msgstr "Prerazporedite dogodke tako, da jih povlečete in spustite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generate recurring events easily."
msgstr "Preprosto ustvarite ponavljajoče se dogodke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organize or attend events using the group scheduling features."
msgstr ""
"Organizirajte ali se udeležite dogodkov z zmožnostmi skupinskega "
"razporejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose among the multiple supported groupware servers."
msgstr "Izbirajte med več podprtimi strežniki skupinske programske opreme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "vCalendar and iCalendar (open standards) native support."
msgstr "Izvorna podpora za vCalendar in iCalendar (odprti standardi)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar merging and import."
msgstr "Združevanje in uvoz koledarjev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag-and-drop between open calendars."
msgstr "Povleci in spusti med odprtimi koledarji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Embedding collaboration with &konqueror;."
msgstr "Vdelava sodelovanja s &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizable icon sets."
msgstr "Prilagodljive zbirke ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag-and-drop tool panels."
msgstr "Povleci in spusti orodne plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Much more..."
msgstr "Veliko več..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now take a <link linkend=\"five-minute-course\">Five-minute fly-over course</"
"link> of &korganizer;, or delve into <link linkend=\"managing-data\">the "
"documentation</link>!"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj pa opravite <link linkend=\"five-minute-course\">petminutni hitri "
"tečaj</link> &korganizer;, ali pa se poglobite v <link linkend=\"managing-"
"data\">dokumentacijo</link>!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Five-minute Fly-over Course of &korganizer;"
msgstr "Petminutni hitri tečaj &korganizer;"

#. Tag: subtitle
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "(for the experienced and for the impatient)"
msgstr "(za izkušene in za nepotrpežljive)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressed for time? Let's get you kick-started with a fast, hands-on overview "
"of &korganizer;!"
msgstr "V stiski s časom? Začnimo s hitrim praktičnim pregledom &korganizer;!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you ever worked with a personal information program before, you'll be "
"right at home with &korganizer;. You can enter new events, reschedule "
"existing events, assign tags to your events, devise new tags, enter and "
"modify lists of attendees and their roles, email event invitations "
"automatically and exchange data with other &korganizer; calendars, create to-"
"dos and write journal entries."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že kdaj delali s programom za osebne podatke, boste kmalu doma z "
"&korganizer;. Vnesete lahko nove dogodke, prestavite obstoječe dogodke, "
"dodelite oznake vašim dogodkom, pripravite nove oznake, vnesete in "
"spreminjate sezname udeležencev in njihovih vlog, samodejno pošiljate vabila "
"na dogodke po e-pošti in izmenjujete podatke z drugimi &korganizer; "
"koledarju, ustvarite opravila in pišete vnose v dnevnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This course assumes that you know how to work with the &kde;, and that you "
"prefer to explore on your own. Only the basic functions of &korganizer; are "
"covered here."
msgstr ""
"Ta tečaj predvideva, da znate delati z &kde; in da raje raziskujte sami. "
"Samo osnovne zmožnosti &korganizer; so zajete tukaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Events"
msgstr "Vnašanje dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"calendar-agenda.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Agenda</guibutton> toolbar button or choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agenda</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item. This will bring up the <link linkend=\"agenda-view"
"\"><guilabel>Agenda View</guilabel> </link>."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-"
"agenda.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Agenda</guibutton> gumb v orodni vrstici ali "
"izberite meni <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agenda</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> To bo prikazalo <link linkend=\"agenda-view"
"\"><guilabel>Pogled Agende</guilabel> </link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the desired date in the <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-"
"date-navigator\">Date Navigator</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na želeni datum v <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-date-"
"navigator\">krmilniku datumov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the text area beside the desired hour in the main panel that reflects "
"the time of the event. Double click this area, or just start typing a "
"summary of the event to open the <guilabel>New Event</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite besedilno območje poleg želene ure na glavni plošči, ki odraža čas "
"dogodka. Dvokliknite to območje ali preprosto začnite tipkati povzetek "
"dogodka, da odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Nov dogodek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">Enter event details</link>. Use the "
"six tabs at the bottom of the window to move around the dialog and access "
"all the event's characteristics."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">Vnesite podrobnosti dogodka</link>. "
"Uporabitešest zavihkov na dnu okna za premikanje po pogovornem oknu in "
"dostop do vseh  značilnosti dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to save the event."
msgstr "Pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> , da shranite dogodek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering To-dos"
msgstr "Vnašanje opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <xref linkend=\"menu-actions-new-todo\"/> menu item to open the "
"<guilabel>New To-do</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element menija <xref linkend=\"menu-actions-new-todo\"/>, da "
"odpretePogovorno okno <guilabel>Novo opravilo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">Enter the to-do details</link>. Use "
"the five tabs at the bottom of the window to move around the dialog and "
"access all the event's characteristics."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">Vnesite podrobnosti o opravilih</"
"link>. Uporabapet zavihkov na dnu okna za premikanje po pogovornem oknu "
"indostop do vseh značilnosti dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to save the to-do."
msgstr "Pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da shranite opravilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Journal Entries"
msgstr "Dodajanje vnosov v dnevnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"journal-new."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Journal</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to open the <link linkend=\"journal-view"
"\"><guilabel>Journal</guilabel> main view</link>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"journal-new."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dnevnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> točko menija, da odprete "
"<link linkend=\"journal-view\"><guilabel>Dnevnik</guilabel> glavni pogled</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Journal</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nov dnevnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter journal entry summary and text."
msgstr "Vnesite povzetek in besedilo v dnevnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rescheduling Events"
msgstr "Prerazporeditev dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rescheduling events is a simple drag-and-drop operation:"
msgstr "Prerazporeditev dogodkov je preprosta operacija povleci in spusti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-date-navigator\">Date "
"Navigator</link> go to the date of the event that you want to reschedule."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba krmilnika datumov <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-date-"
"navigator\">Navigator</link> da greste na datum dogodka, ki ga želite "
"prestaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should choose an appropriate <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view"
"\">view</link> before beginning this operation. Only the <link linkend="
"\"agenda-view\"><guilabel>Agenda</guilabel> view </link> (Day, Work Week and "
"Week views) shows individual hours and are suitable for rescheduling exactly-"
"timed events (appointments), while the Month view only shows days. Therefore "
"the Month view is most suitable for long-term events like holidays."
msgstr ""
"Izbrati morate ustrezen <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view\">pogled</link> "
"pred začetkom te operacije. Samo <link linkend=\"agenda-view"
"\"><guilabel>Pogled dnevnega reda</guilabel> </link> (dan, delovni teden in "
"tedenski pogledi) prikazujejo posamezne ure in so primerni za natančno "
"prerazporejanje časovno omejenih dogodkov (sestanke), medtem ko pogled "
"meseca prikazuje samo dneve. Zato je mesečni pogled najbolj primeren za "
"dolgoročne dogodke, kot so prazniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display the Week view select the Agenda view, press the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-week.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Week</"
"guibutton> view toolbar button, or choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Week</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz tedenskega pregleda  izberite pogled Agenda, "
"pritisnite<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"calendar-week.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Teden</guibutton> gumb orodne vrstice ali "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teden</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> točko menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and drop the event to the new date and time location."
msgstr "Povlecite in spustite dogodek na novo lokacijo datuma in ure."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to reschedule more precisely, double-click the event and change "
"the start and end time using the drop down menus that divide the day into "
"quarter hours. If that is not precision enough, you can enter the desired "
"time directly."
msgstr ""
"Če želite natančneje prestaviti termin, dvokliknite dogodek in "
"spremenitezačetni in končni čas z uporabo spustnih menijev, ki dan razdelijo "
"načetrt ure. Če to ni dovolj natančno, lahko vnesete želeni čas neposredno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rescheduling or Editing To-dos"
msgstr "Prerazporejanje ali urejanje opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should choose an appropriate <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view"
"\">view</link> before beginning this operation. Only the <link linkend="
"\"todo-view\"><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"calendar-tasks.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>To-do List</guilabel> view </link> and <link "
"linkend=\"description-view\">the To-do View sidebar component </link> show "
"to-dos which do not have a due date."
msgstr ""
"Izbrati morate primerni <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view\">pogled</link> "
"pred začetkom te operacije. Samo pogled <link linkend=\"todo-view"
"\"><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-tasks."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guilabel>seznam "
"opravil</guilabel></link> in <link linkend=\"description-view\">stranska "
"komponenta operavi </link> prikazujejo opravila, ki še niso potekla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display the To-do List view, press the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-tasks.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guibutton>To-do List</guibutton> view "
"toolbar button, or choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>To-do List</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz pogleda seznama opravil pritisnite "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-tasks.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guibutton>pogled "
"seznama opravil</guibutton>orodni vrstici ali izberite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seznam opravil</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reschedule a to-do, right click it. This will bring up a context menu. "
"Choose the <guimenuitem>Copy to</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Move to</"
"guimenuitem> menu items and select the new date from the calendar now "
"appearing. The to-do is now copied or moved to the selected date. "
"Alternatively, if the main panel holds a <guilabel>To-do List</guilabel> "
"view, just right click the column <guilabel>Due Date/Time</guilabel>. A "
"calendar will appear instantly, allowing you to set the new due date."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prestaviti opravilo, ga kliknite z desno miškino tipko. To bo "
"prikazalo kontekstni meni. Izberite elemente menija <guimenuitem>Kopiraj v</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Premakni v</guimenuitem>  in zdaj izberite nov "
"datum iz koledarja, ki se je pojavil. Opravilo je zdaj kopirano ali "
"premaknjeno na izbrani datum.Druga možnost je, da glavna plošča vsebuje "
"pogled <guilabel>Seznam opravil</guilabel>, z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"stolpec <guilabel>Datum/čas</guilabel>. Takoj se bo prikazal koledar in vam "
"bo omogočil nastavitev nov datum poteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">edit a to-do</link>, right click it "
"and choose the <guimenuitem>Edit...</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">urediti opravilo</link>, ga "
"kliknite z desno miškino tipko in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Uredi...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Zaključek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This five-minute course covered only the basic operation of &korganizer;. "
"Now you should go on and read the rest of this manual to unleash the full "
"power of &korganizer;'s capabilities. But if you do not feel like it, you "
"should at least skip through the <link linkend=\"faq\">&FAQ;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta petminutni tečaj je zajemal samo osnovno delovanje &korganizer;. Zdaj bi "
"morali nadaljevati in prebrati preostanek tega priročnika, da boste v celoti "
"sprostili moč zmožnosti &korganizer;ja. Ampak, če se vam ne da, bi morali "
"vsaj preskočiti do <link linkend=\"faq\">&FAQ;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing, Exporting, and Managing Calendars"
msgstr "Uvoz, izvoz in upravljanje koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; can store (and retrieve) events, journal entries and to-dos "
"using various methods, and to different locations. Each of these locations "
"is called a <firstterm>calendar resource</firstterm>."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; lahko shranjuje (in pridobiva) dogodke, vnose v dnevnik in "
"opravilaz različnimi metodami in na različne lokacije. Vsaka od teh lokacij "
"se imenuje <firstterm>vir koledarja</firstterm>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; supports calendar files based on standards such as iCalendar "
"and vCalendar natively (adding them as new resources), but you can import "
"the data (merge) into an existing resource and open the file in a new window "
"too. Importing files in the format used by the old <application>ical</"
"application> application is also supported."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; podpira koledarske datoteke, ki izvirno temeljijo na "
"standardih, kot je iCalendar in vCalendar (dodajte jih kot nove vire), "
"vendar lahko uvozite podatke (in združite) v obstoječi vir in odprete "
"datoteko v tudi novem oknu. Uvažanje datotek v formatu, ki ga je uporabljal "
"stari <application>ical</application> je tudi podprto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export your data as an iCalendar or vCalendar file. These files are "
"supported by most scheduling applications."
msgstr ""
"Podatke lahko izvozite kot datoteko iCalendar ali vCalendar. Te datoteke "
"sopodpira večina aplikacij za razporejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter we will explain how to manage your calendar resources as "
"well as using the import and export actions."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju bomo razložili, kako upravljati vire koledarja ter kako "
"uporabljati dejanja uvoza in izvoza."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar Resources"
msgstr "Viri koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; uses a local file as its default resource. But this is not your "
"only option: there are several other resources you can add: groupware "
"servers, journal entries as blogs, network files, &etc; If you use more than "
"one resource, &korganizer; <link linkend=\"config-main-general-personal"
"\">can be configured to use the default resource or ask which resource to "
"use</link> when saving new events, to-dos or journal entries. &korganizer; "
"will seamlessly merge the items from two or more resources in the <link "
"linkend=\"description-view\">views</link>."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; uporablja lokalno datoteko kot privzeti vir. Ampak to ni vaša "
"edina možnost: obstaja več drugih virov, ki jih lahko dodate: strežniki "
"skupinske programske opreme, vnosi v dnevnike kot blogi, omrežne datoteke "
"itd. Če uporabljate več kot en vir, lahko  &korganizer; <link linkend="
"\"config-main-general-personal\">konfigurirate tako, da uporabite privzeti "
"vir ali vprašate, kateri vir želite uporabiti</link> pri shranjevanju novih "
"dogodkov, opravil ali vnosov v dnevnik. &korganizer; bo neopazno združil "
"elemente iz dveh ali več virov v <link linkend=\"description-view\">poglede</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default resource is a good choice for many use cases, but you may want "
"to use another resource, especially if you use a supported groupware server. "
"Please ask the server administrator for the information required to "
"configure the groupware resource, including free/busy information publishing "
"and retrieving. Access to free/busy information allows an event organizer to "
"take the attendee's calendar into consideration when adding him to the "
"event's attendee list."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti vir je dobra izbira za številne primere uporabe, vendar boste morda "
"želeli za uporabo drugega vira, še posebej, če uporabljate podprt strežnik "
"skupinske programske opreme. Vprašajte skrbnika strežnika za potrebne "
"informacije za konfiguriranje vira skupinske programske opreme, vključno z "
"objavo informacij o prostem/zasedenem času in pridobivanje. Dostop do "
"informacij o zasedenosti omogoča organizatorju dogodka, daupošteva koledar "
"udeleženca, ko ga dodate v seznam udeležencev dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides calendar storage, groupware servers typically offer contacts, mail "
"and <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-freebusy\">free/busy "
"information</link> storage. Therefore, some of the resources discussed here "
"may be related to other resources from &kmail; and &kaddressbook; (the mail "
"and contacts components of &kontact;), or to the <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"free-busy\">free/busy settings in the main configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Poleg shranjevanja koledarja strežniki skupinske programske opreme običajno "
"ponujajo stike, pošto in <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm=\"gloss-freebusy"
"\">shranjevanje informacij  o prost/zaseden času</link>. Zato so nekateri "
"viri, o katerih se tukaj razpravlja morda povezana z drugimi viri iz &kmail; "
"in &kaddressbook; (pošta in kontaktne komponente &kontact;), ali na <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-free-busy\">nastavitve prost/zaseden v glavni "
"konfiguraciji</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that &korganizer; <link linkend=\"group-scheduling\">group "
"scheduling</link> communication is based on a peer to peer email standard. "
"This means that you do not need a groupware server to use it!"
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da &korganizer; komunikacijo o <link linkend=\"group-scheduling"
"\">skupnem razporejanju</link> temelji na e-poštnem standardu enakovrednih "
"članov. To pomeni, da za uporabo ne potrebujete strežnika za skupinsko "
"programsko opremo!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Add Calendars dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za dodajanje koledarjev "
"&korganizer;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Add Calendars dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za dodajanje koledarjev v "
"&korganizer;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Add Calendars dialog</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za dodajanje koledarjev v "
"&korganizer;</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a New &korganizer; Resource"
msgstr "Dodajanje novega vira v &korganizer; Vir"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &korganizer;'s settings dialog with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &korganizer;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"and select the <guilabel>Calendars</guilabel> tab from the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogovorno okno z nastavitvami &korganizer; z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&korganizer;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Koledarji</guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively open the context menu in the <guilabel>Calendar Manager</"
"guilabel> sidebar with a &RMB; click and select <guilabel>Add Calendar...</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa odprete kontekstni meni v <guilabel>Upravljalniku koledarja</"
"guilabel> stranska vrstica z &RMB; kliknite in izberite <guilabel>Dodaj "
"koledar...</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Calendar Manager</guilabel> is not displayed on the "
"sidebar, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Sidebar</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show Calendar Manager</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to display it."
msgstr ""
"Če <guilabel>Upravljalnik koledarja</guilabel> ni prikazan nastranski "
"vrstici izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>stranska vrstica</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži "
"element menija upravljalnika koledarja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za prikaz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button to add new resources to the "
"list of available resources."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj ...</guibutton>, da dodate nove vire "
"vseznam razpoložljivih virov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the resource to enable it."
msgstr "Izberite vir, da ga omogočite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Later, if you want to edit or delete a resource, select it on the "
"<guilabel>Calendar Manager</guilabel> sidebar and press <guibutton>Delete "
"Calendar</guibutton> to delete it or <guibutton>Calendar Properties...</"
"guibutton> to modify it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pozneje urediti ali izbrisati vir, ga izberite na stranska vrstici "
"<guilabel>Upravljalnik koledarja</guilabel> in pritisnite <guibutton>Izbriši "
"koledar</guibutton>, da ga izbrišete, ali <guibutton>Lastnosti koledarja...</"
"guibutton>, da ga spremenite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Among the existing resources, you can find in &korganizer;:"
msgstr "Med obstoječimi viri lahko v &korganizer; najdete:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Birthdays &amp; Anniversaries"
msgstr "Rojstni dnevi &amp; obletnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides access to birthday and anniversary dates of contacts in your "
"address book as calendar events."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča dostop do rojstnih dni in datumov obletnic stikov v vašem imeniku "
"kot koledarskih dogodkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "DAV groupware resource"
msgstr "Vir skupinske programske opreme DAV"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resource to manage DAV calendars and address books (CalDAV, GroupDAV)."
msgstr "Vir za upravljanje koledarjev in imenikov DAV (CalDAV, GroupDAV)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Google Calendars and Tasks"
msgstr "Google koledarji in opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access your Google Calendars and Tasks."
msgstr "Dostopajte do svojih Google koledarjev in opravil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "iCal Calendar File"
msgstr "koledarska datoteka iCal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loads data from an iCal file."
msgstr "Naloži podatke iz datoteke iCal."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "iCal Calendar Folder"
msgstr "mapa koledarja iCal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides access to calendar items, each stored in a single file, in a given "
"directory."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča dostop do elementov koledarja, od katerih je vsak shranjen v eni "
"datoteki v danem imeniku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "KAlarm Calendar File"
msgstr "Koledarska datoteka KAlarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loads data from a KAlarm calendar file."
msgstr "Naloži podatke iz koledarske datoteke KAlarm."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "KAlarm Calendar Directory"
msgstr "Imenik koledarjev KAlarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loads data from a local KAlarm folder."
msgstr "Naloži podatke iz lokalne mape KAlarm."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kolab Groupware Server"
msgstr "Strežnik Kolab Groupware"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides access to Kolab groupware folders and e-mail on a Kolab IMAP Server."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča dostop do map Kolab groupware in e-pošte na strežniku Kolab IMAP."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open-Xchange Groupware Server"
msgstr "Open-Xchange Groupware Server"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides access to the appointments, tasks, and contacts of an Open-Xchange "
"groupware server."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča dostop do sestankov, nalog in stikov strežnika skupinske programske "
"opreme Open-Xchange."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing, Exporting and Maintaining Calendars"
msgstr "Uvoz, izvoz in vzdrževanje koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While local files are just one among many other resources that can be used "
"by &korganizer;, they are the most convenient way to share calendars, save "
"copies, or import items from your old calendar program."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko so lokalne datoteke le eden izmed mnogih drugih virov, ki jih "
"lahko uporablja &korganizer;, so najpriročnejši način za skupno rabo "
"koledarjev, shranjevanje kopij ali uvoz elementov iz vašega starega "
"koledarskega programa.Medtem ko so lokalne datoteke le eden izmed mnogih "
"drugih virov, ki jih lahko uporablja &korganizer;, so najpriročnejši način "
"za skupno rabo koledarjev, shranjevanje kopij ali uvoz elementov iz vašega "
"starega koledarskega programa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Calendars"
msgstr "Uvoz koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have an iCalendar or vCalendar file, and you would like to import it, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import Calendar...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu "
"item. &korganizer; will ask you if you want to <guilabel>Add as new "
"calendar</guilabel>, which adds the calendar file as a new local file "
"resource or <guilabel>Merge into existing calendar</guilabel>, which merges "
"the calendar items into an existing resource."
msgstr ""
"Če imate datoteko iCalendar ali vCalendar in bi jo radi uvozili, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvozi</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi koledar...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> element "
"menija. &korganizer; vas bo vprašal, ali želite <guilabel>Dodaj kot nov "
"koledar</guilabel>, ki doda koledarsko datoteko kot nov lokalni datotečni "
"vir ali <guilabel>Združi v obstoječi koledar</guilabel>, ki spoji elemente "
"koledarja v obstoječi vir."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A good time to do this would be if you received a vCalendar with a few "
"entries via email, for instance, or if you are planning to import your "
"calendar from another application. In the latter case, the first thing to do "
"is to use that application to export the calendar data in one of the formats "
"above, or use a tool to convert from the application's native format."
msgstr ""
"Pravi čas za to bi bil, če bi na primer po e-pošti prejeli vCalendar z nekaj "
"vnosi ali če nameravate svoj koledar uvoziti iz druge aplikacije. V slednjem "
"primeru morate najprej uporabiti to aplikacijo za izvoz koledarskih podatkov "
"v eni od zgornjih oblik zapisa ali uporabiti orodje za pretvorbo iz izvorne "
"oblike zapisa aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting Calendars"
msgstr "Izvoz koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export your data as an iCalendar file, which is supported by most "
"scheduling applications. &korganizer; will export all calendar items from "
"the enabled (checked) resources which are <link linkend=\"filters-view\">not "
"filtered out</link> (let's call these items <quote>active</quote> items). In "
"other words, if you cannot see a calendar item, it won't be in the exported "
"file. To filter out the undesired items before exporting them, you can "
"create <link linkend=\"filters-view\">filters</link>. Filters are even more "
"effective if you classify your events and to-dos with <link linkend="
"\"categories-view\">tags</link>. To enable and disable resources, check or "
"uncheck the resource box in the <link linkend=\"managing-resources"
"\"><guilabel>Calendar Manager</guilabel> </link> sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Podatke lahko izvozite kot datoteko iCalendar, ki jo podpira večina "
"aplikacij za razporejanje. &korganizer; bo izvozil vse elemente koledarja iz "
"omogočenih (označenih) virov, ki <link linkend=\"filters-view\">niso "
"izločeni</link> (te elemente imenujemo <quote>aktivni</quote> elementi). Z "
"drugimi besedami, če ne vidite koledarskega elementa, ga ne bo v izvoženi "
"datoteki. Če želite filtrirati neželene elemente, preden jih izvozite, lahko "
"ustvarite <link linkend=\"filters-view\">filtre</link>. Filtri so še "
"učinkovitejši, če svoje dogodke in opravila razvrstite z <link linkend="
"\"categories-view\">oznakami</link>. Če želite omogočiti ali onemogočiti "
"vire, potrdite ali počistite polje vira v stranski vrstici <link linkend="
"\"managing-resources\"><guilabel>Upravitelj koledarja</guilabel> </link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export all your <quote>active</quote> events, to-dos and journal entries "
"(independent of to what resource they belong) as a new iCalendar file, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Export as iCalendar...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"menu item. The <guilabel>Save As</guilabel> dialog will pop up. Enter the "
"file name and location for the new file to complete the export action."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti vse svoje <quote>aktivne</quote> dogodke, opravila in "
"vnose v dnevnik (ne glede na to, kateremu viru pripadajo) kot novo datoteko "
"iCalendar, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu "
">Izvozi</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi kot iCalendar ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> element menija. Odpre se pogovorno okno <guilabel>Shrani kot</"
"guilabel>. Vnesite ime datoteke in lokacijo za novo datoteko, da dokončate "
"dejanje izvoza."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maintaining Your Calendars"
msgstr "Vzdrževanje vaših koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contemporary computers have ample storage space. However, if you synchronize "
"your &korganizer; calendar with a limited-memory machine like the Palm "
"device, you will find archiving useful. The performance of &korganizer; can "
"also become worse when there are many events. To archive old items, follow "
"the procedure below:"
msgstr ""
"Sodobni računalniki imajo dovolj prostora za shranjevanje. Vendar, če "
"sinhronizirate &korganizer; koledar z napravo z omejenim pomnilnikom, kot je "
"naprava Palm, se vam bo zdelo arhiviranje koristno. Delovanje &korganizer; "
"se lahko tudi poslabša, ko je veliko dogodkov. Če želite arhivirati stare "
"predmete, sledite spodnjemu postopku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive Old "
"Incidences...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Arhiviraj stare primere ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill in the date in <guilabel>Archive now items older than</guilabel> field "
"or use the Calendar Widget to choose the date. Alternatively, you can "
"automatically archive all items older than a certain period of time."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite datum v polje <guilabel>Arhiviraj zdaj elemente, starejše od</"
"guilabel> ali uporabite gradnik za koledar, da izberete datum. Lahko pa "
"samodejno arhivirate vse elemente, starejše od določenega časovnega obdobja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have chosen archiving, you must also provide a filename for the "
"archive in the <guilabel>Archive File</guilabel> field. If you want to reuse "
"an older archive file, press the <guilabel>Open file dialog</guilabel> "
"button and find an existing archive. The entries will be added to the file, "
"so any item already in the file will not be modified."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali arhiviranje, morate podati tudi ime datoteke za arhiv v polju "
"<guilabel>Arhivska datoteka</guilabel>. Če želite ponovno  uporabiti "
"starejšo arhivsko datoteko, pritisnite gumb <guilabel>Odpri pogovorno okno "
"datoteke</guilabel> in poiščite obstoječi arhiv. Vnosi bodo dodani v "
"datoteko, tako da noben element, ki je že v datoteki, ne bo spremenjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archiving will keep all old items in a file, including completed to-dos. But "
"if you do not want to keep completed to-dos at all, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Purge Completed To-dos</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item to remove all the completed to-dos from "
"your active resources. If you want to keep your completed to-dos, but do not "
"wish to view them in the to-do lists, consider <link linkend=\"filters-view"
"\">filtering them out</link> instead of purging them."
msgstr ""
"Arhiviranje bo ohranilo vse stare elemente v datoteki, vključno z "
"dokončanimi opravili. Če pa dokončanih opravil sploh ne želite obdržati, "
"izberite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Počisti dokončana opravila</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, "
"da odstranite vsa dokončana opravila iz vaših aktivnih virov. Če želite "
"obdržati dokončana opravila, vendar si jih ne želite ogledati na seznamih "
"opravil, jih <link linkend=\"filters-view\">filtrirajte</link>, namesto da "
"bi jih izbrisali."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Views and Filters"
msgstr "Pogledi in filtri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While calendars (resources) can hold events, to-dos and/or journal entries, "
"these items are very different in nature. To-dos may have no date associated "
"with them, so a schedule view is not suitable to them. Journal entries are a "
"collection your reflections, occurrences or experiences. They require their "
"own view mode, as they are not related with the list of upcoming events or "
"the list of to-dos, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko koledarji (viri) lahko vsebujejo dogodke, opravila in/ali vnose v "
"dnevnik, so ti predmeti po naravi zelo različni. Opravila morda nimajo "
"povezanega datuma, zato pogled urnika zanje ni primeren. Dnevniški zapisi so "
"zbirka vaših razmišljanj, dogodkov ali izkušenj. Potrebujejo svoj način "
"pogleda, saj niso povezani s seznamom prihajajočih dogodkov ali seznamom "
"opravil &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To solve the challenge of displaying your information in a useful and "
"intuitive fashion, &korganizer; offers different views, filters and search "
"capabilities. You can also assign tags to related events and to-dos, which "
"will help you to view them later, using filters or colors."
msgstr ""
"Za rešitev izziva prikaza vaših informacij na uporaben in intuitiven način "
"je &korganizer; ponuja različne poglede, filtre in možnosti iskanja. Oznake "
"lahko dodelite tudi povezanim dogodkom in opravilom, kar vam bo pomagalo, da "
"si jih ogledate pozneje z uporabo filtrov ali barv."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer; Views"
msgstr "&korganizer; Pogledi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section, we describe the different view modes, and present an "
"overview of how to browse your personal data using &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku opisujemo različne načine pogleda in predstavljamo pregled, "
"kako brskati po svojih osebnih podatkih z &korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &korganizer; window can be divided into two main areas: the main window "
"and the sidebar. The main window displays the main views and the sidebar "
"displays the Date Navigator, the To-do View, the Item Viewer and the "
"Calendar Manager View. To show or hide the sidebar components, check or "
"uncheck the menu items under the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Sidebar</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; okno lahko razdelimo na dve glavni področji: glavno okno in "
"stransko vrstico. V glavnem oknu so prikazani glavni pogledi, stranska "
"vrstica pa Krmar po datumih, Pogled opravil, Pregledovalnik elementov in "
"Pogled upravitelja koledarja. Če želite prikazati ali skriti komponente "
"stranske vrstice, označite ali počistite menijske elemente v podmeniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Stranska vrstica</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Date Navigator is provided to browse and select dates. Today's date will "
"be outlined with a small box, dates which have events scheduled on them will "
"be bold (daily or weekly recurring events may not be marked as bold, <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-views\">depending on the view configuration</link>), "
"and holidays will be colored red. If you want to jump to a date, simply "
"click on it. Hold down the mouse to select multiple contiguous dates at "
"once. The <guilabel>What's Next</guilabel>, <guilabel>List</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Agenda</guilabel> and <guilabel>Journal</guilabel> views will only "
"show events, to-dos or journals items from the dates selected in the Date "
"Navigator. The <guilabel>Month</guilabel> view will show events or to-dos "
"from the first month shown in the Date Navigator (the selected days in the "
"month won't change the Month view, only month changes)."
msgstr ""
"Navigator po datumih je na voljo za brskanje in izbiro datumov. Današnji "
"datum bo označen z majhnim okvirčkom, datumi, ki imajo načrtovane dogodke, "
"bodo krepki (dnevni ali tedenski ponavljajoči se dogodki morda ne bodo "
"označeni kot krepki, <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">odvisno od "
"konfiguracije pogleda </link>), prazniki pa bodo obarvani rdeče. Če želite "
"skočiti na datum, preprosto kliknite nanj. Držite miško, da izberete več "
"sosednjih datumov hkrati. Pogledi <guilabel>Kaj je naslednje</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Seznam</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dnevni red</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Dnevnik</guilabel> bodo prikazali samo dogodke, opravila ali "
"elemente dnevnika iz datume, izbrane v Krmarju po datumih. Pogled "
"<guilabel>Mesec</guilabel> bo prikazal dogodke ali opravila iz prvega "
"meseca, ki so prikazani v Krmarju po datumih (izbrani dnevi v mesecu ne bodo "
"spremenili pogleda meseca, spremeni se le mesec)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The To-do View sidebar component lists your to-dos, just like the <link "
"linkend=\"todo-view\">To-do view</link>. It is useful if you want to see "
"your to-dos while using the other views."
msgstr ""
"Komponenta stranske vrstice pogleda opravil navaja vaša opravila, tako kot "
"<link linkend=\"todo-view\">pogled opravil</link>. Uporabno je, če želite "
"med uporabo drugih pogledov videti svoja opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Item Viewer sidebar component shows details of the currently selected "
"events, to-dos or journal entries."
msgstr ""
"Komponenta stranske vrstice pregledovalnika predmetov prikazuje podrobnosti "
"o trenutno izbranih dogodkih, opravilih ali vnosih v dnevnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, Calendar Manager Viewer sidebar component allow you to enable or "
"disable the resources on the list, by checking or unchecking the resource "
"box, and to manage your resources. For more information, please check <xref "
"linkend=\"managing-resources\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu vam komponenta stranske vrstice Pregledovalnik upravitelja "
"koledarja omogoča, da omogočite ali onemogočite vire na seznamu, tako da "
"potrdite ali počistite polje za vir, in upravljate svoje vire. Za več "
"informacij preverite <xref linkend=\"managing-resources\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also browse your calendar view by choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Backward</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item (or pressing the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-previous.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>toolbar button), which "
"goes to the previous day, week, month or year, choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item (or pressing the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>toolbar button), which goes to the next day, week, month "
"or year (depending on the view), or choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>To Today</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item (or "
"pressing the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-jump-"
"today.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>toolbar "
"button), which will include the current day in the current view."
msgstr ""
"Po pogledu koledarja lahko tudi brskate tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menijski element (ali pritisnete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-previous.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>gumb orodne vrstice), ki "
"se pomakne na prejšnji dan, teden, mesec ali leto, pri čemer izberete "
"element menija<menuchoice><guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naprej</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (ali pritisk <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject >gumb orodne vrstice), ki se pomakne na naslednji dan, "
"teden, mesec ali leto (odvisno od pogleda), ali izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Na danes</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice > menijski element (ali pritisk <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"go-jump-today.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>gumb orodne vrstice), ki bo vključeval trenutno dan v "
"trenutnem pogledu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's Next View"
msgstr "Kaj je naslednje Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view displays events and to-dos in a simple format you can quickly "
"read. All open to-dos will be displayed, but only the events from the days "
"selected in the <guilabel>Date Navigator</guilabel> sidebar will be shown. "
"Events and to-dos are displayed one per line."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled prikazuje dogodke in opravila v preprosti obliki, ki jo lahko "
"hitro preberete. Prikazana bodo vsa odprta opravila, prikazani pa bodo samo "
"dogodki iz dni, izbranih v stranski vrstici <guilabel>Datumski navigator</"
"guilabel>. Dogodki in opravila so prikazani po eno na vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to the What's Next view by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>What's Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite na pogled Kaj je naslednje tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kaj je naslednje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Event List View"
msgstr "Pogled seznama dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view displays all your to-dos, events and journal entries for the dates "
"selected in the Date Navigator as a list. Open to-dos that are not due on "
"the selected dates are not shown. This view is good for displaying many "
"different items in a compact fashion. It is also useful if your events are "
"spread out over a long time period that would not be displayed completely on "
"the screen when using one of the other views."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled prikazuje vsa vaša opravila, dogodke in vnose v dnevnik za datume, "
"izbrane v Krmarju po datumih, kot seznam. Odprta opravila, ki niso zapadla "
"na izbrane datume, niso prikazana. Ta pogled je primeren za prikaz številnih "
"različnih predmetov na strnjen način. Uporabno je tudi, če so vaši dogodki "
"razporejeni v daljšem časovnem obdobju, ki ne bi bilo v celoti prikazano na "
"zaslonu, če uporabljate enega od drugih pogledov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The items are displayed one per line. Columns show if a reminder is set (a "
"bell icon displayed in it means the reminder is set), if it repeats multiple "
"times (a chasing-arrows icon means a repeating event), the start and end "
"time information. Hovering the mouse over an item will bring up a tooltip "
"with detailed information about the item."
msgstr ""
"Postavke so prikazane po ena na vrstico. Stolpci prikazujejo, ali je opomnik "
"nastavljen (ikona zvonca, prikazana v njem, pomeni, da je opomnik "
"nastavljen), če se ponavlja večkrat (ikona s preslednimi puščicami pomeni "
"ponavljajoči se dogodek), informacije o začetnem in končnem času. Če miško "
"premaknete nad element, se prikaže opis orodja s podrobnimi informacijami o "
"predmetu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the list view by choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Event List</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite prikaz na pogled seznama tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seznam dogodkov</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "Agenda View"
msgstr "Pogled dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Agenda view presents your events or due to-dos for one or more days, "
"sorted chronologically. You can also see the length of each event in the day "
"timetable. To enable the Agenda view choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agenda</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or press "
"the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-"
"agenda.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>toolbar "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Pogled dnevnega reda prikazuje vaše dogodke ali dolžnosti za en ali več dni, "
"razvrščene kronološko. V dnevnem urniku lahko vidite tudi dolžino "
"posameznega dogodka. Če želite omogočiti pogled dnevnega reda, izberite "
"menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dnevni "
"red</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pritisnite "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar- agenda."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>gumb orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Day</guilabel>, <guilabel>Work Week</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Week</guilabel> views are variations of the Agenda view. In fact, "
"you can set the days shown in the Agenda view at any time by selecting them "
"in the Date Navigator."
msgstr ""
"Pogledi <guilabel>Dan</guilabel>, <guilabel>Delovni teden</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Teden</guilabel> so različice pogleda Dnevni red. Pravzaprav lahko "
"kadar koli nastavite dneve, prikazane v pogledu Dnevni red, tako da jih "
"izberete v Krmarju po datumih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Time is indicated by a time bar on the left side of the view. A scrollbar on "
"the right is provided when the whole day cannot be displayed on a single "
"screen (which is the usual case). Each rectangle in the view represents an "
"individual event or to-do due for that time, and displays the start and end "
"time and summary. A <guiicon>bell</guiicon> icon is displayed if a reminder "
"is set, and a <guiicon>chasing-arrows</guiicon> icon is displayed if it "
"repeats multiple times. Hovering the mouse over an calendar item will bring "
"up a tooltip with the item detailed information. To make &korganizer; show a "
"red line marking the current-time on the current day (the Marcus Bains "
"line), check the <guilabel>Show current-time (Marcus Bains) line</guilabel> "
"box in the <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; view "
"configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Čas je označen s časovno vrstico na levi strani pogleda. Drsni trak na desni "
"je na voljo, ko celega dneva ni mogoče prikazati na enem zaslonu (kar je "
"običajno). Vsak pravokotnik v pogledu predstavlja posamezen dogodek ali "
"opravilo za ta čas ter prikazuje začetni in končni čas ter povzetek. Ikona "
"<guiicon>zvonec</guiicon> je prikazana, če je nastavljen opomnik, in ikona "
"<guiicon>puščice za lov</guiicon> je prikazana, če se opomnik ponovi "
"večkrat. Če miško premaknete nad koledarsko postavko, se prikaže opis orodja "
"s podrobnimi informacijami o tem elementu. Če želite narediti &korganizer; "
"pokažite rdečo črto, ki označuje trenutni čas na trenutni dan (črta Marcus "
"Bains), označite polje <guilabel>Prikaži vrstico trenutnega časa (Marcus "
"Bains)</guilabel> v <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; ogled "
"konfiguracije</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any event can be re-sized with your mouse. Simply move the mouse pointer "
"near the top or bottom edge of the event, and drag the edge up or down. This "
"way you can visually modify the starting and ending time of your event. This "
"also works in the Week and Work Week views. In other words, it is possible "
"to change start and end times with the mouse by just moving the upper or "
"lower border of the event to the new time."
msgstr ""
"Vsakemu dogodku lahko spremenite velikost z miško. Preprosto premaknite "
"kazalec miške blizu zgornjega ali spodnjega roba dogodka in povlecite rob "
"navzgor ali navzdol. Tako lahko vizualno spremenite začetni in končni čas "
"vašega dogodka. To deluje tudi v pogledu Teden in Delovni teden. Z drugimi "
"besedami, z miško je mogoče spremeniti začetni in končni čas tako, da samo "
"premaknete zgornjo ali spodnjo mejo dogodka na nov čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any event can be rescheduled with your mouse. Move the mouse pointer over "
"the event, and drag it to a new time location. This also works in the Week "
"and Work Week views. Events can be moved to other, presently non-visible "
"dates. Move the mouse pointer over the event, and drag it to the Date "
"Navigator."
msgstr ""
"Vsak dogodek lahko prestavite z miško. Premaknite kazalec miške nad dogodek "
"in ga povlecite na novo časovno lokacijo. To deluje tudi v pogledu Teden in "
"Delovni teden. Dogodke lahko premaknete na druge, trenutno nevidne datume. "
"Kazalec miške premaknite nad dogodek in ga povlecite v Krmar po datumih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the Agenda view cannot contain the whole day on most screens, you will "
"have to scroll up and down to see the whole day. There is a useful hint that "
"tells you if there are any currently invisible events above or below your "
"current view; it is a small down-pointing arrow at the bottom of each day "
"view or up-pointing arrow at the top."
msgstr ""
"Vsak dogodek lahko prestavite z miško. Premaknite kazalec miške nad dogodek "
"in ga povlecite na novo časovno lokacijo. To deluje tudi v pogledu Teden in "
"Delovni teden. Dogodke lahko premaknete na druge, trenutno nevidne datume. "
"Kazalec miške premaknite nad dogodek in ga povlecite v Krmar po datumih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two useful shortcuts for adding events:"
msgstr "Obstajata dve uporabni bližnjici za dodajanje dogodkov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click any open region of time, and &korganizer; will automatically "
"create an event with default duration (which is customizable in the "
"preferences dialog). You can immediately add the summary. The events "
"<quote>snap</quote> to half-hour increments, rounding off to the closest "
"half hour from where you clicked."
msgstr ""
"Dvakrat kliknite poljubno odprto časovno območje in &korganizer; bo "
"samodejno ustvaril dogodek s privzetim trajanjem (ki ga je mogoče "
"prilagoditi v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami). Povzetek lahko dodate takoj. "
"Dogodki se <quote>zaskočijo</quote> v polurnih korakih in zaokrožijo na "
"najbližje pol ure od mesta, kjer ste kliknili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select any open region of time, and double click it or start writing the "
"summary of the event. &korganizer; will automatically set the duration and "
"start time as defined by the selection area in the Agenda view."
msgstr ""
"Izberite poljubno odprto časovno območje in ga dvakrat kliknite ali začnite "
"pisati povzetek dogodka. &korganizer; samodejno nastavi trajanje in začetni "
"čas, kot je določeno v izbirnem območju v pogledu dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips for improved event viewing:"
msgstr "Nasveti za boljši ogled dogodkov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the shift-wheel shortcut for growing/shrinking the hourly grid row "
"height. This is useful for seeing event details if you have several events "
"occurring in the same time interval."
msgstr ""
"Za povečanje/zmanjšanje višine vrstice urne mreže uporabite bližnjico Shift-"
"kolesce. To je uporabno za ogled podrobnosti dogodkov, če se v istem "
"časovnem intervalu zgodi več dogodkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show the timelabels on both sides of the hourly grid by selecting Show/Hide "
"Right-side Time Labels on the timelabels context menu."
msgstr ""
"Časovne oznake na obeh straneh urne mreže prikažite tako, da v kontekstnem "
"meniju časovnih oznak izberete možnost Prikaži/skrij časovne oznake na desni "
"strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you organize your agenda, the color of the events reflect their "
"tags, and depending on the <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; "
"view configuration</link>, it may also reflect its <link linkend=\"managing-"
"resources\">resource</link>. Therefore, if you assign <link linkend="
"\"categories-view\">tags to events</link> and <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"colors\">different colors to tags</link> , you will be able to quickly "
"identify the type of event by its color."
msgstr ""
"Za lažje organiziranje dnevnega reda barva dogodkov odraža njihove oznake in "
"glede na <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; pogled "
"konfiguracije</link>, lahko odraža tudi njegov <link linkend=\"managing-"
"resources\">vir</link>. Torej, če dodelite <link linkend=\"categories-view"
"\">oznake dogodkom</link> in <link linkend=\"config-main-colors\">različne "
"barve oznakam</link>, boste lahko hitro prepoznati vrsto dogodka po njegovi "
"barvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Agenda view can display events from all your calendars merged into one "
"view or show a view per calendar. Having both views available via tabs is "
"also possible and can be <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">customized in "
"the preferences dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Pogled dnevnega reda lahko prikaže dogodke iz vseh vaših koledarjev, "
"združenih v en pogled, ali prikaže pogled na koledar. Oba pogleda sta na "
"voljo prek zavihkov in ju lahko <link linkend=\"config-main-views"
"\">prilagodite v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid "Day View"
msgstr "Dnevni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view presents the <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Agenda view</link> for "
"a single day."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled predstavlja <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">pogled dnevnega reda</"
"link> za en dan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Day view by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Day</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or pressing "
"the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-jump-today.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Day</guilabel> "
"button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon preklopite na dnevni pogled tako, da izberete menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dan</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali pritisnete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"go -jump-today.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Dan</guilabel> gumb v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next X Days View"
msgstr "Pogled naslednjih X dni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view presents the <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Agenda view</link> for "
"the next days, starting from today. You can change the number of days to be "
"displayed in the <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; view "
"configuration</link>. The default value is 3."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled predstavlja <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">pogled dnevnega reda</"
"link> za naslednje dni, začenši z današnjim dnem. Spremenite lahko število "
"dni, ki bodo prikazani v <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; "
"ogled konfiguracije</link>. Privzeta vrednost je 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the next days view by choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next X Days</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, (X represents the number of days, usually 3)."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite prikaz na pogled naslednjih dni tako, da izberete menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednjih X dni</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (X predstavlja število dni, običajno 3) ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid "Week View"
msgstr "Tedenski pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Week view provides a view similar to the Day view. Events for seven days "
"are shown next to each other."
msgstr ""
"Tedenski pogled ponuja pogled, podoben dnevnemu pogledu. Dogodki za sedem "
"dni so prikazani drug poleg drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Week view by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Week</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or pressing "
"the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-week."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Week</"
"guilabel> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon preklopite na tedenski pogled tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teden</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali pritisnete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"view -calendar-week.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Teden</guilabel> gumb v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid "Work Week View"
msgstr "Pogled delovnega tedna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the same as the Week view, except that it shows only the working "
"days of the week."
msgstr ""
"To je enako kot tedenski pogled, le da prikazuje samo delovne dni v tednu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Work Week view by choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Work Week</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite zaslon na pogled delovnega tedna tako, da izberete element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delovni teden</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Month View"
msgstr "Mesečni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Month view shows all the events and due to-dos for the current month in "
"a familiar month calendar layout. Each cell in the view represents a day, "
"and each day contains all of the events that can fit in the area provided "
"(maximizing the window will enable you to see more appointments). "
"Information on repeating and reminder status is indicated through "
"<guiicon>bell</guiicon> and <guiicon>chasing arrows</guiicon> icons, just as "
"in other views."
msgstr ""
"Mesečni pogled prikazuje vse dogodke in dolžnosti za tekoči mesec v znani "
"postavitvi mesečnega koledarja. Vsaka celica v pogledu predstavlja dan in "
"vsak dan vsebuje vse dogodke, ki se lahko prilegajo v ponujeno območje "
"(maksimiranje okna vam bo omogočilo ogled več sestankov). Informacije o "
"stanju ponavljanja in opomnika so označene z ikonami <guiicon>zvonec</"
"guiicon> in <guiicon>puščice za lov</guiicon>, tako kot v drugih pogledih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate the Month view using the Date Navigator arrows, or the items and "
"toolbar buttons from the <guilabel>Go</guilabel> menu. Since the visible "
"area of a day cell may not contain all events and to-dos, you can use the "
"keyboard to browse the items, or you can use the scrollbars to see all the "
"events and to-dos from that day."
msgstr ""
"Krmarite po pogledu meseca s puščicami Krmarja po datumih ali z elementi in "
"gumbi orodne vrstice v meniju <guilabel>Pojdi</guilabel>. Ker vidno območje "
"dnevne celice morda ne vsebuje vseh dogodkov in opravil, lahko s tipkovnico "
"brskate po elementih ali pa uporabite drsne trakove, da si ogledate vse "
"dogodke in opravila tega dne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:861 index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hover your mouse over any calendar item to display a tooltip with the item "
"details. Double click an empty area to create an event, double click any "
"calendar item to edit it."
msgstr ""
"Z miško se pomaknite nad kateri koli element koledarja, da se prikaže opis "
"orodja s podrobnostmi o elementu. Dvakrat kliknite prazno območje, da "
"ustvarite dogodek, dvakrat kliknite kateri koli element koledarja, da ga "
"uredite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you organize your data, the color of the events may reflect their "
"tags, and their <link linkend=\"managing-resources\">resource</link>, "
"depending on the <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">&korganizer; view "
"configuration</link>. Therefore, if you assign <link linkend=\"categories-"
"view\">tags to events</link> and <link linkend=\"config-main-colors"
"\">different colors to tags</link>, you can identify the type of event (or "
"resource) by its color."
msgstr ""
"Za lažje organiziranje podatkov lahko barva dogodkov odraža njihove oznake "
"in njihov <link linkend=\"managing-resources\">vir</link>, odvisno od <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-views\"> &korganizer; ogled konfiguracije</link>. "
"Torej, če dodelite <link linkend=\"categories-view\">oznake dogodkom</link> "
"in <link linkend=\"config-main-colors\">različne barve oznakam</link>, lahko "
"prepoznate vrsto dogodek (ali vir) po barvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:874
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Month view by choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Month View</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item or pressing the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-month.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Month</"
"guilabel> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon preklopite na mesečni pogled tako, da izberete menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mesečni pogled</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pritisnete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-month.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Mesec</"
"guilabel> gumb v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timeline View"
msgstr "Pogled časovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Timeline view shows all events for the selected timespan in a gantt "
"view. Every calendar is displayed in a separate line."
msgstr ""
"Pogled časovne osi prikazuje vse dogodke za izbrano časovno obdobje v "
"gantotečnem pogledu. Vsak koledar je prikazan v ločeni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid "To-do List"
msgstr "Seznam opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The To-do List provides a place for you to jot down quick (or long-term) "
"notes about things that need to be done. The To-do View sidebar component "
"appears right below the Date Navigator. You can also display it in the main "
"panel if you click the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"view-calendar-tasks.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>To-do List</guilabel> view toolbar button or if "
"you choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>To-do List</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Seznam opravkov ponuja mesto, kjer si lahko zapisujete hitre (ali "
"dolgoročne) zapiske o stvareh, ki jih je treba narediti. Komponenta stranske "
"vrstice pogleda opravil se prikaže tik pod navigatorjem po datumih. Lahko ga "
"prikažete tudi na glavni plošči, če kliknete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-tasks.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guilabel> Ogled "
"seznama opravil</guilabel> gumb orodne vrstice ali če izberete menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Seznam opravil</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give your to-do a <quote>date due</quote>, in other words a date "
"when the to-do should be finished."
msgstr ""
"Opravilu lahko določite <quote>datum</quote>, z drugimi besedami, datum, ko "
"naj bo opravilo končano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also assign priorities to to-dos, and they will appear sorted in "
"order of priority. The lower the number, the higher the priority, except "
"that zero (0) is defined as <quote>no priority.</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Opravilom lahko dodelite tudi prioritete in prikazana bodo razvrščena po "
"prednostnem vrstnem redu. Nižje kot je število, višja je prioriteta, le da "
"je nič (0) definirana kot <quote>brez prioritete.</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make a new to-do entry, right click the To-do View sidebar component, or "
"the To-do List view, and choose the <guimenuitem>New To-do</guimenuitem> "
"menu item. If you right click an already existing to-do, you will get more "
"choices: you can <guimenuitem>Show</guimenuitem> the summary, "
"<guimenuitem>Edit...</guimenuitem> the to-do details, <guimenuitem>Delete</"
"guimenuitem> the to-do altogether, or you can create a <guimenuitem>New Sub-"
"To-do...</guimenuitem> You could for example make a large to-do like "
"building a house, and make sub-to-dos like choosing the right building site, "
"hiring an architect, hiring workers and finally arranging a party for your "
"friends."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti nov vnos opravil, z desno tipko miške kliknite komponento "
"stranske vrstice pogleda opravil ali pogled seznama opravil in izberite "
"element menija <guimenuitem>Novo opravilo</guimenuitem>. Če z desno miškino "
"tipko kliknete že obstoječe opravilo, boste imeli več možnosti: "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži</guimenuitem> povzetek, <guimenuitem>Uredi ...</"
"guimenuitem> podrobnosti opravila, <guimenuitem> Izbrišite</guimenuitem> "
"opravilo v celoti ali pa ustvarite <guimenuitem>Novo podopravilo ...</"
"guimenuitem> Ustvarite lahko na primer veliko opravilo, kot je gradnja hiše, "
"in naredite pod -opravila, kot je izbira pravega gradbišča, najem arhitekta, "
"najem delavcev in končno organizacija zabave za vaše prijatelje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose <guimenuitem>New To-do...</guimenuitem>, a dialog will pop "
"up, allowing you to enter all necessary <link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do"
"\">information</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete <guimenuitem>Novo opravilo ...</guimenuitem>, se prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča vnos vseh potrebnih <link linkend=\"entering-"
"data-to-do\">informacij</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click any to-do in the list to highlight it. If you click the thick-line box "
"on the left of the to-do description, you will change the <quote>completed</"
"quote> status of the to-do. If you double-click the to-do description, you "
"will be able to edit all its details."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite katero koli opravilo na seznamu, da ga označite. Če kliknete polje "
"z debelo črto na levi strani opisa opravila, boste spremenili status "
"<quote>dokončano</quote> opravila. Če dvakrat kliknete opis opravila, boste "
"lahko uredili vse njegove podrobnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also pick <link linkend=\"managing-purge-archive\">Purge Completed</"
"link> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button menu to delete "
"all to-do entries that you have marked completed."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi <link linkend=\"managing-purge-archive\">Čiščenje "
"končano</link> v meniju miškinega gumba <mousebutton>desna</mousebutton>, da "
"izbrišete vsa opravila, ki ste jih označili kot dokončana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To-dos can also be dragged around with the mouse to rearrange the hierarchy "
"or to exchange to-dos with other calendar windows. You can also read an "
"<link linkend=\"other-features-drag-and-drop\">overview</link> of all "
"available drag-and-drop operations."
msgstr ""
"Opravila lahko tudi povlečete z miško, da preuredite hierarhijo ali "
"izmenjate opravila z drugimi okni koledarja. Preberete lahko tudi <link "
"linkend=\"other-features-drag-and-drop\">pregled</link> vseh razpoložljivih "
"operacij povleci in spusti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "Journal View"
msgstr "Pogled dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Journal view provides a place for you to record your reflections, "
"occurrences or experiences. You can display the Journal view in the main "
"panel if you press the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"journal-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Journal View</guilabel> toolbar button or if you "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Journal</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Pogled Dnevnik ponuja prostor za beleženje vaših razmišljanj, dogodkov ali "
"izkušenj. Pogled dnevnika lahko prikažete na glavni plošči, če pritisnete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"journal-new.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guilabel>dnevnik Gumb "
"orodne vrstice Pogled</guilabel> ali če izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dnevnik</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guilabel>New journal ...</guilabel> link (or the "
"<guibutton>New Journal ...</guibutton> button), a new journal entry will be "
"created. If you want to edit a journal entry, just click the text box and "
"edit it! To remove a journal entry, press the <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>delete button in the Journal view."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete povezavo <guilabel>Nov dnevnik ...</guilabel> (ali gumb "
"<guibutton>Nov dnevnik ...</guibutton>), bo ustvarjen nov vnos v dnevnik. Če "
"želite urediti vnos v dnevnik, samo kliknite besedilno polje in ga uredite! "
"Če želite odstraniti vnos v dnevnik, pritisnite gumb <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>izbriši v pogledu dnevnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Tags</title>"
msgstr "<title>Oznake</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you organize your entries in related groups, you can assign tags to "
"events, to-dos and journal entries. If you assign tags, you can use them "
"later when searching, filtering, and displaying events and to-dos."
msgstr ""
"Za lažje organiziranje vnosov v sorodnih skupinah lahko dodelite oznake "
"dogodkom, opravilom in vnosom v dnevnik. Če dodelite oznake, jih lahko "
"pozneje uporabite pri iskanju, filtriranju in prikazovanju dogodkov in "
"opravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To assign tags when editing or creating new <link linkend=\"entering-data-"
"events-general\">events</link> or <link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do-general"
"\">to-dos</link>, click the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button in the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab. You can assign more than one tag to each "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Za dodeljevanje oznak pri urejanju ali ustvarjanju novih <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events-general\">dogodkov</link> ali <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-to-do-general\">opravil</link > kliknite gumb <guibutton>..."
"</guibutton> na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>. Vsakemu elementu lahko "
"dodelite več kot eno oznako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create and delete tags, choose the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Tags...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item to "
"open the <guilabel>Manage Tags</guilabel> dialog. If you assign <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-colors\">different colors to tags</link>, you will be "
"able to quickly identify the type of event by its color, either in the "
"Agenda view or in the Month view (depending on the <link linkend=\"config-"
"main-views\">&korganizer; view configuration</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti in izbrisati oznake, izberite menijski element "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje oznak ..."
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Upravljanje oznak</guilabel> . Če <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"colors\">oznakam dodelite različne barve</link>, boste lahko hitro "
"prepoznali vrsto dogodka po barvi, bodisi v pogledu dnevnega reda bodisi v "
"pogledu meseca ( odvisno od <link linkend=\"config-main-views"
"\">konfiguracije pogleda &korganizer;</link>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filtri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To help you view, find and export your data, you can create and use filters "
"for your calendars. For instance, if you do not want to view completed to-"
"dos, you can filter them out, instead of <link linkend=\"managing-purge-"
"archive\">purging them</link>. If you assign tags, you can use them to "
"create filters."
msgstr ""
"Za pomoč pri ogledu, iskanju in izvozu podatkov lahko ustvarite in uporabite "
"filtre za svoje koledarje. Če si na primer ne želite ogledati dokončanih "
"opravil, jih lahko filtrirate, namesto da bi jih <link linkend=\"managing-"
"purge-archive\">počistili</link>. Če dodelite oznake, jih lahko uporabite za "
"ustvarjanje filtrov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create, delete and edit filters, choose the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage View Filters...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> menu item to open the <guilabel>Edit Calendar Filters</"
"guilabel> dialog. Using this dialog, you can create, delete and edit filters "
"that will affect which items will be displayed by &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti, izbrisati in urediti filtre, izberite menijski element "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje filtrov "
"pogleda ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, da odprete <guilabel>Urejanje "
"filtrov koledarja</guilabel> pogovorno okno. V tem pogovornem oknu lahko "
"ustvarjate, brišete in urejate filtre, ki bodo vplivali na elemente, ki jih "
"bo prikazal &korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> submenu and the filter toolbar drop down offer access to all "
"available filters created using the <link linkend=\"menu-settings-edit-"
"filters\"><guilabel>Edit Calendar Filters</guilabel></link> dialog. To "
"toggle the display of the filters toolbar on and off, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Filters Toolbar</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If you "
"do not want to use any filter, choose <guilabel>No filter</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Podmeni <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> in spustni meni orodne vrstice filtrov ponujata "
"dostop do vseh razpoložljivih filtrov, ustvarjenih z uporabo <link linkend="
"\"menu-settings-edit-filters\"><guilabel>Pogovorno okno Uredi filtre "
"koledarja</guilabel></link>. Za vklop in izklop prikaza orodne vrstice "
"filtrov izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Prikazane orodne vrstice</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Orodno vrstico "
"filtrov</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če ne želite uporabiti nobenega filtra, "
"izberite <guilabel>Brez filtra</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filters are useful when <link linkend=\"managing-export\">exporting your "
"calendar</link>. If you use a filter, only the filtered (visible) items will "
"be exported. Also, filters are more effective when the items are already "
"classified and organized in <link linkend=\"categories-view\">tags</link>, "
"as you can easily create filters based on tags."
msgstr ""
"Filtri so uporabni pri <link linkend=\"managing-export\">izvažanju "
"koledarja</link>. Če uporabite filter, bodo izvoženi samo filtrirani (vidni) "
"elementi. Poleg tega so filtri učinkovitejši, ko so elementi že razvrščeni "
"in organizirani v <link linkend=\"categories-view\">oznakah</link>, saj "
"lahko enostavno ustvarite filtre na podlagi oznak."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching"
msgstr "Iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or press the <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap> </keycombo> shortcut to find events, to-dos, or "
"journal entries by their to summaries, descriptions, and/or tags. The find "
"action will only search the specified fields."
msgstr ""
"Izberite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Najdi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap> </keycombo> bližnjica za iskanje "
"dogodkov, opravil ali vnosov v dnevnik po njihovih povzetkih, opisih in/ali "
"oznakah. Dejanje iskanja bo preiskalo samo navedena polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use wildcards if you do not remember the exact summary. If you do "
"not know a single character of the summary, put <userinput>?</userinput> "
"instead of the missing character. If you do not know more characters, use "
"<userinput>*</userinput>. For instance if you know that the event or to-do "
"has <emphasis>meeting</emphasis> in the beginning and <emphasis>product</"
"emphasis> after, you would write <userinput>meeting*product</userinput> in "
"the Find dialog. &korganizer; will locate entries like <quote>To-do: arrange "
"meeting about the new product</quote>, <quote>Meeting to discuss the old "
"product line</quote> and similar. Letter case is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Če se ne spomnite natančnega povzetka, lahko uporabite nadomestne znake. Če "
"ne poznate niti enega znaka povzetka, namesto manjkajočega znaka vnesite "
"<userinput>?</userinput>. Če ne poznate več znakov, uporabite <userinput>*</"
"userinput>. Če na primer veste, da ima dogodek ali opravilo "
"<emphasis>sestanek</emphasis> na začetku in <emphasis>izdelek</emphasis> za "
"njim, bi napisali <userinput>sestanek*izdelek</userinput> v Najdi pogovorno "
"okno. &korganizer; bo našel vnose, kot so <quote>Opravila: dogovorite "
"sestanek o novem izdelku</quote>, <quote>Sestanek za razpravo o stari liniji "
"izdelkov</quote> in podobno. Velike črke so prezrte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1049
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result of the Find operation is a list of events, journal entries and/or "
"to-dos with the specified keyword. The search list characteristics are the "
"same as the <link linkend=\"list-view\">List View</link>."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat operacije Najdi je seznam dogodkov, vnosov v dnevnik in/ali opravil "
"z določeno ključno besedo. Značilnosti iskalnega seznama so enake kot <link "
"linkend=\"list-view\">Pogled seznama</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This resulting list is active. You can double-click a line to display or "
"edit the event or to-do details. Get more information about these details in "
"<xref linkend=\"entering-data-events\"/> and <xref linkend=\"entering-data-"
"to-do\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastali seznam je aktiven. Če želite prikazati ali urediti podrobnosti "
"dogodka ali opravila, lahko dvokliknete vrstico. Več informacij o teh "
"podrobnostih najdete v <xref linkend=\"entering-data-events\"/> in <xref "
"linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Data"
msgstr "Vnos podatkov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Dogodki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Events are future or past appointments, like business meetings, personal "
"anniversaries and cinema visits. An event can also take several days, like "
"holidays."
msgstr ""
"Dogodki so prihodnji ali pretekli sestanki, kot so poslovni sestanki, osebni "
"jubileji in obiski kina. Dogodek lahko traja tudi več dni, na primer "
"prazniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1073
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering a new event is very easy. Just choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Event...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. A window with six tabs at the bottom "
"will appear."
msgstr ""
"Vstop v nov dogodek je zelo enostaven. Preprosto izberite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov dogodek ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže se okno s šestimi zavihki na dnu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you wish you can use a different way to create a new event:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite, lahko uporabite drugačen način za ustvarjanje novega dogodka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the Date Navigator to go to the event date."
msgstr "Uporabite Navigator po datumu, da se pomaknete na datum dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to <guilabel>Agenda</guilabel> view and click the desired view's icon "
"on the <guimenu>View Toolbar</guimenu> or select the desired view from the "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu. Since your event starts at a particular time, "
"you should choose a <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view\">view</link> that "
"displays hours of the day. You may choose <guimenuitem>Day</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Work Week</guimenuitem> view or <guimenuitem>Week</guimenuitem> "
"view. The <guimenuitem>Month</guimenuitem> view is more suitable for to-dos, "
"described below."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite na pogled <guilabel>Dnevni red</guilabel> in kliknite ikono "
"želenega pogleda v <guimenu>Orodni vrstici Pogled</guimenu> ali izberite "
"želeni pogled v meniju <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu>. Ker se vaš dogodek začne ob "
"določeni uri, bi morali izbrati <link linkend=\"reference-menus-view"
"\">pogled</link>, ki prikazuje ure v dnevu. Izberete lahko pogled "
"<guimenuitem>Dan</guimenuitem>, pogled <guimenuitem>Delovni teden</"
"guimenuitem> ali pogled <guimenuitem>Teden</guimenuitem>. Pogled "
"<guimenuitem>Mesec</guimenuitem> je bolj primeren za opravila, opisana "
"spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the main panel, double click the time and date when your event starts."
msgstr "Na glavni plošči dvakrat kliknite čas in datum začetka dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A dialog with six tabs at the bottom of the window appears. Enter your data "
"as described below."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno s šestimi zavihki na dnu okna. Vnesite svoje "
"podatke, kot je opisano spodaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &korganizer; pogovornega okna za urejanje "
"dogodka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za urejanje dogodka &korganizer;</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za urejanje dogodka &korganizer;</"
"para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a thorough description of the individual event window fields and "
"widgets. Not all fields have to be filled in; some can be left empty. Read "
"the <link linkend=\"entering-data-required-fields\">Required fields</link> "
"section for detailed information. And if you prefer to learn by example, "
"there's one in the <link linkend=\"examples-entering-event\">Entering event</"
"link> section."
msgstr ""
"To je natančen opis polj in gradnikov posameznih oken dogodkov. Ni treba "
"izpolniti vseh polj; nekatere lahko pustimo prazne. Preberite razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"entering-data-required-fields\">Zahtevana polja</link> za podrobne "
"informacije. In če se raje učite z zgledom, je v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"examples-entering-event\">Dogodek vstopa</link> na voljo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Summary:"
msgstr "Povzetek:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a short description of the event into the <guilabel>Summary</guilabel> "
"field. This description is the text shown on the &korganizer; main panel."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite kratek opis dogodka v polje <guilabel>Povzetek</guilabel>. Ta opis "
"je besedilo, prikazano na &korganizer; glavna plošča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location:"
msgstr "Lokacija:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter short description of the <guilabel>location</guilabel> where the event "
"will take place."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite kratek opis <guilabel>lokacije</guilabel>, kjer bo dogodek potekal."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Start</guilabel> and <guilabel>End</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Začetek</guilabel> in <guilabel>Konec</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &korganizer; suggested Start and End dates of your event. Events are "
"expected to start and end on the same date. Change these dates as desired. "
"Enter the dates directly or use the <link linkend=\"glossary\" endterm="
"\"gloss-calendar-widget\"> Calendar Widget</link>. Select the time from "
"quarter hour intervals, or enter the desired time directly into the time "
"fields. These fields are only available when the <guilabel>All Day</"
"guilabel> box is not checked."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; predlagani začetni in končni datum vašega dogodka. Dogodki se "
"bodo predvidoma začeli in končali na isti datum. Spremenite te datume po "
"želji. Datume vnesite neposredno ali uporabite <link linkend=\"glossary\" "
"endterm=\"gloss-calendar-widget\"> Pripomočki za koledar</link>. Izberite "
"čas med četrturnimi intervali ali vnesite želeni čas neposredno v časovna "
"polja. Ta polja so na voljo le, če polje <guilabel>Ves dan</guilabel> ni "
"potrjeno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1144 index.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Splošno"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details:"
msgstr "Podrobnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a long description of the event in the large, untitled rectangle. You "
"can write as many details as you wish here. For example, If the event is, "
"say, planned general repair of your car, you can list all items that need "
"repairing. Later on you can print this list and hand it over to the "
"serviceman. If the event is shopping, you should list the goods that you "
"need to buy. Print the event and take it to the shop with you."
msgstr ""
"V velik pravokotnik brez naslova vnesite dolg opis dogodka. Tukaj lahko "
"napišete kolikor želite podrobnosti. Na primer, če je dogodek, recimo, "
"načrtovano generalno popravilo vašega avtomobila, lahko navedete vse "
"predmete, ki jih je treba popraviti. Kasneje lahko ta seznam natisnete in ga "
"predate serviserju. Če je dogodek nakupovanje, morate navesti blago, ki ga "
"morate kupiti. Natisnite dogodek in ga odnesite s seboj v trgovino."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1159 index.docbook:2433
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Tags</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Oznake</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can assign several <link linkend=\"categories-view\">tags</link> to a "
"calendar item. Click the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button to display all "
"available tags. Check the tag boxes to assign suitable tags to the event."
msgstr ""
"Koledarskemu elementu lahko dodelite več <link linkend=\"categories-view"
"\">oznak</link>. Kliknite gumb <guibutton>...</guibutton>, da prikažete vse "
"razpoložljive oznake. Potrdite polja za oznake, da dogodku dodelite ustrezne "
"oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also add a new tag, modify a tag, or delete a tag in the "
"<guilabel>Manage Tags</guilabel> dialog. Open this dialog with <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Tags</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko dodate novo oznako, spremenite oznako ali izbrišete oznako v "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Upravljanje oznak</guilabel>. Odprite to pogovorno "
"okno z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje "
"oznak</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your language lesson at work may belong to both Business and Education tags, "
"while the anniversary of your marriage belongs to either Personal or Special "
"Occasion - it is your choice."
msgstr ""
"Vaša jezikovna lekcija v službi lahko sodi med poslovne in izobraževalne "
"oznake, obletnica poroke pa med osebne ali posebne priložnosti - izbira je "
"vaša."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access:"
msgstr "Dostop:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Public</guilabel>, <guilabel>Private</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Confidential</guilabel> to keep the event private or confidential. "
"Currently, this choice correctly sets the <quote>CLASS</quote> attribute of "
"the events to <quote>PUBLIC</quote>, <quote>PRIVATE</quote> or "
"<quote>CONFIDENTIAL</quote>. However, whether these settings are really used "
"to restrict the access of the information depends on the client and/or "
"groupware server implementation."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Javno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zasebno</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Zaupno</guilabel>, da dogodek ostane zaseben ali zaupen. Trenutno "
"ta izbira pravilno nastavi atribut <quote>CLASS</quote> dogodkov na "
"<quote>PUBLIC</quote>, <quote>PRIVATE</quote> ali <quote>CONFIDENTIAL</"
"quote>. Toda ali se te nastavitve res uporabljajo za omejevanje dostopa do "
"informacij, je odvisno od implementacije strežnika odjemalca in/ali "
"programske opreme skupine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently, &korganizer; <emphasis>will</emphasis> display items owned by "
"other people and marked as confidential. Other clients may treat them "
"differently, but be careful when publishing private or confidential events: "
"iCalendar is a text file format, and can be read with any text editor (if "
"someone has read access to them). So if you want to keep items really "
"confidential, make sure you use a resource that only you can access."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno &korganizer; <emphasis>bo</emphasis> prikazal predmete, ki so v "
"lasti drugih ljudi in so označeni kot zaupni. Drugi odjemalci jih lahko "
"obravnavajo drugače, vendar bodite previdni pri objavljanju zasebnih ali "
"zaupnih dogodkov: iCalendar je format besedilne datoteke in ga je mogoče "
"brati s katerim koli urejevalnikom besedil (če ima nekdo dostop za branje do "
"njih). Torej, če želite, da so predmeti zares zaupni, poskrbite, da boste "
"uporabili vir, do katerega imate dostop samo vi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attendees Tab"
msgstr "Udeleženci Zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose in this tab the people you want to invite to your event."
msgstr "V tem zavihku izberite ljudi, ki jih želite povabiti na svoj dogodek."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attendees "
"tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje "
"dogodka – zavihek Udeleženci</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attendees tab</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje dogodka – "
"zavihek Udeleženci</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attendees tab</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje dogodka – "
"zavihek Udeleženci</para>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Meeting Organizer:"
msgstr "Organizator srečanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the identity corresponding to the organizer of this to-do or event. If "
"&korganizer; is configured to send invitation emails, the identity selected "
"on this combo box will be used when sending these emails. The default "
"identity can be set in the <guilabel>Personal</guilabel> section of the "
"&korganizer; configuration. In addition, identities are gathered from your "
"&kmail; settings and from your address book."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi identiteto, ki ustreza organizatorju tega opravila ali dogodka. Če "
"&korganizer; je konfiguriran za pošiljanje e-poštnih sporočil z vabili, bo "
"pri pošiljanju teh e-poštnih sporočil uporabljena identiteta, izbrana v tem "
"kombiniranem polju. Privzeto identiteto lahko nastavite v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Osebno</guilabel> v &korganizer; konfiguracijo. Poleg tega se "
"identitete zbirajo iz vašega &kmail; nastavitve in iz imenika."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attendee list"
msgstr "Seznam udeležencev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list in the center of the tab displays the attendees selected for this "
"event, and lets you add attendees by entering the name and mail address, "
"edit or remove them."
msgstr ""
"Seznam na sredini zavihka prikazuje udeležence, izbrane za ta dogodek, in "
"vam omogoča, da dodate udeležence z vnosom imena in e-poštnega naslova, jih "
"uredite ali odstranite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the attendee(s) are in your Address Book, you do not have to remember or "
"type his email address to add it to the attendee list. Just click the "
"<guibutton>Select Addressee...</guibutton> button and choose the attendee(s) "
"from the list. Please note that this is the standard &kde; address book, "
"which is also used by &kmail; and can also be called as a separate "
"application (&kaddressbook;)."
msgstr ""
"Če so udeleženci v vašem imeniku, vam ni treba zapomniti ali vnesti "
"njegovega e-poštnega naslova, da ga dodate na seznam udeležencev. Preprosto "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Izberi naslovnika ...</guibutton> in s seznama "
"izberite udeleženca(-e). Upoštevajte, da je to standardni &kde; imenik, ki "
"ga uporablja tudi &kmail; in ga lahko pokličete tudi kot ločeno aplikacijo "
"(&kaddressbook;)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Participants"
msgstr "Udeleženci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the role of the attendee (Participant, Optional Participant, "
"Observer, Chair) from the drop down menu at the left side of an entry. The "
"role is a simple reminder of what part the attendee plays in this event."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju na levi strani vnosa izberite vlogo udeleženca "
"(udeleženec, neobvezni udeleženec, opazovalec, predsednik). Vloga je "
"preprost opomnik o tem, kakšno vlogo ima udeleženec v tem dogodku."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the status of the attendee (Needs Action, Accepted, Declined, "
"Tentative, Delegated) from the drop down menu at the right side of an entry. "
"If you use groupware schedule and request responses from your attendees, as "
"you receive the responses the status of the attendee will be updated. If you "
"do not request responses, you will have to update the status manually."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju na desni strani vnosa izberite status udeleženca (Potrebno "
"je ukrepanje, Sprejeto, Zavrnjeno, Pogojno, Pooblaščeno). Če uporabljate "
"urnik programske opreme skupine in zahtevate odgovore svojih udeležencev, se "
"bo status udeleženca posodobil, ko boste prejeli odgovore. Če ne zahtevate "
"odgovorov, boste morali status posodobiti ročno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Request Response"
msgstr "Zahtevaj odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Request Response</guilabel> from the drop down box if this "
"attendee should respond to your schedule plan. Consequently the attendee "
"will be emailed with the event schedule information. A small envelope will "
"appear in the details list to indicate this. This feature is specially "
"useful when groupware scheduling is enabled, as the attendee's status is "
"updated automatically."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju izberite <guilabel>Zahtevaj odgovor</guilabel>, če naj se "
"ta udeleženec odzove na vaš načrt urnika. Posledično bo udeleženec prejel e-"
"pošto z informacijami o urniku dogodka. Na seznamu s podrobnostmi se bo "
"pojavila majhna ovojnica, ki to označuje. Ta funkcija je še posebej "
"uporabna, ko je omogočeno razporejanje skupinske programske opreme, saj se "
"status udeleženca samodejno posodobi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reminder Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek opomnik"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reminder"
msgstr "Opomin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a default reminder in the drop down box and press <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton> if &korganizer; should remind you about an event."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju izberite privzeti opomnik in pritisnite <guibutton>Dodaj</"
"guibutton>, če &korganizer; vas mora spomniti na dogodek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> button to open the <guilabel>Edit "
"existing reminder</guilabel> dialog. Using this dialog, you can choose how "
"many minutes, hours or days before or after the events start or end you want "
"to be reminded, you can set repeating intervals for your reminders, and "
"create special reminders that display text or play sounds."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj</guibutton>, da odprete pogovorno "
"okno <guilabel>Uredi obstoječi opomnik</guilabel>. V tem pogovornem oknu "
"lahko izberete, koliko minut, ur ali dni pred ali po začetku ali koncu "
"dogodkov želite biti opomnjeni, lahko nastavite ponavljajoče se intervale za "
"svoje opomnike in ustvarite posebne opomnike, ki prikazujejo besedilo ali "
"predvajajo zvoke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurrence tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Ponavljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some events take place regularly. You can specify their exact scheduling "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri dogodki potekajo redno. Njihov natančen urnik lahko določite tukaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Recurrence "
"tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje "
"dogodka – zavihek Ponavljanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Recurrence tab</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje dogodka – "
"zavihek Ponavljanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Recurrence tab</"
"para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje dogodka – "
"zavihek Ponavljanje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the settings, start by selecting a recurrence rule at the right "
"of <guilabel>Repeats</guilabel> from the drop down box. If <guilabel>Never</"
"guilabel> is selected, you are not able to make any changes on this tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati nastavitve, začnite z izbiro pravila ponavljanja na "
"desni strani <guilabel>Ponavljanja</guilabel> v spustnem polju. Če je "
"izbrana možnost <guilabel>Nikoli</guilabel>, na tem zavihku ne morete "
"narediti nobenih sprememb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurrence Rule"
msgstr "Pravilo ponavljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose if you want to repeat this event daily, weekly, monthly or yearly. "
"More detailed options are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali želite ta dogodek ponavljati dnevno, tedensko, mesečno ali "
"letno. Podrobnejše možnosti so naslednje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "Dnevno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify whether the event occurs every day (1), every other day (2) and so "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Določite, ali se dogodek zgodi vsak dan (1), vsak drugi dan (2) in tako "
"naprej."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "Tedensko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify whether the event occurs every week (1), every other week (2) and so "
"on. Also specify the days (Sunday ... Monday) on which the event occurs."
msgstr ""
"Določite, ali se dogodek zgodi vsak teden (1), vsak drugi teden (2) in tako "
"naprej. Določite tudi dneve (nedelja ... ponedeljek), na katere se dogodek "
"zgodi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Mesečno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can either have the event occur on the same day of the month, or in a "
"specific week on a specific day of the week. You need to choose between "
"these two possibilities. By default, &korganizer; assumes you want to repeat "
"on the same calendar day of the month (for instance the 15th). You can also "
"adjust the period, so you can repeat monthly, tri-monthly and so on."
msgstr ""
"Dogodek lahko nastavite na isti dan v mesecu ali v določenem tednu na "
"določen dan v tednu. Izbirati morate med tema dvema možnostma. Privzeto je "
"&korganizer; predpostavlja, da želite ponoviti na isti koledarski dan v "
"mesecu (na primer 15. Prav tako lahko prilagodite obdobje, tako da lahko "
"ponavljate mesečno, trimesečno in tako naprej."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly"
msgstr "Letno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is similar to Monthly. You need to choose whether or not you are "
"indicating a calendar day of the year (&eg;, the 250th day of the year), in "
"a specific week on a specific day of the week of a month (&eg;, the 2nd "
"Tuesday of March), or the day of the month in a particular month of the "
"year. By default, &korganizer; assumes you mean the day of the month. You "
"can adjust the period to reflect events that occur bi-annually, every four "
"years, and so on."
msgstr ""
"To je podobno Mesečnemu. Izbrati morate, ali želite navesti koledarski dan v "
"letu (&eg; 250. dan v letu) v določenem tednu na določen dan v tednu v "
"mesecu (&eg; 2. torek v marec) ali dan v mesecu v določenem mesecu v letu. "
"Privzeto je &korganizer; predvideva, da mislite na dan v mesecu. Obdobje "
"lahko prilagodite tako, da odraža dogodke, ki se zgodijo dvakrat letno, "
"vsaka štiri leta itd."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurrence Range"
msgstr "Razpon ponavljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, events which repeat will do so forever; there is no <quote>end</"
"quote> to the repetition. This may or may not be desirable, so you are able "
"to terminate the repetition by selecting an end date or a number of "
"occurrences."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se dogodki, ki se ponavljajo, ponavljajo vedno; ponavljanju ni "
"<quote>konca</quote>. To je lahko zaželeno ali ne, tako da lahko prekinete "
"ponavljanje z izbiro končnega datuma ali več ponovitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exceptions"
msgstr "Izjeme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may have a very nice recurrence rule set up, but realize that there are "
"a few exceptions. If you set up your college class schedule for instance, "
"you may want to make exceptions for holidays and the like. In this area, you "
"can add, change, and delete dates from the list of exceptions (&ie; times "
"when even if the recurrence rule matches, the event will <emphasis>not be "
"scheduled</emphasis>). Pick a date with the date selector, and press "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> to include it. For removing dates, highlight them "
"in the box on the right side, and then click <guibutton>Delete</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Morda imate nastavljeno zelo dobro pravilo ponavljanja, vendar se zavedajte, "
"da obstaja nekaj izjem. Če na primer nastavite urnik predavanj na fakulteti, "
"boste morda želeli narediti izjeme za počitnice in podobno. V tem območju "
"lahko dodajate, spreminjate in brišete datume s seznama izjem (&ie; časi, ko "
"dogodek <emphasis>ne bo načrtovan</emphasis>, tudi če se pravilo ponavljanja "
"ujema). Izberite datum z izbirnikom datuma in pritisnite <guibutton>Dodaj</"
"guibutton>, da ga vključite. Če želite datume odstraniti, jih označite v "
"polju na desni strani in kliknite <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attachments"
msgstr "Priponke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Events and to-dos can contain attachments. Attachments can either be stored "
"as links or inline. To add an attachment press the <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Dogodki in opravila lahko vsebujejo priloge. Priloge lahko shranite kot "
"povezave ali v vrstici. Če želite dodati prilogo, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attachments "
"tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje "
"dogodka – zavihek Priloge</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attachments tab</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna &korganizer; za urejanje dogodka – "
"zavihek Priloge</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Attachments tab</"
"para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za urejanje dogodka &korganizer; - "
"zavihek Priloge</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking <guilabel>Store a copy of the attachment file inside the calendar</"
"guilabel> will cause the attachment to be stored inside your calendar, which "
"can take a lot of space depending on the size of the attachment. If this "
"option is not checked, then only a link pointing to the attachment will be "
"stored. Do not use a link for attachments that change often or may be moved "
"(or removed) from their current location."
msgstr ""
"Če odkljukate <guilabel >Shrani kopijo priponke v koledarju</guilabel >, bo "
"priponka shranjena v vaš koledar, kar lahko zavzame veliko prostora, odvisno "
"od velikosti priponke. Če ta možnost ni označena, bo shranjena samo "
"povezava, ki kaže na prilogo. Ne uporabljajte povezave za priloge, ki se "
"pogosto spreminjajo ali se lahko premaknejo (ali odstranijo) s trenutne "
"lokacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following actions in the context menu are provided to work with "
"attachments:"
msgstr ""
"Za delo s prilogami so na voljo naslednja dejanja v kontekstnem meniju:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Odprto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the selected attachment with the associated application."
msgstr "Prikaži izbrano prilogo s povezano aplikacijo."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save As..."
msgstr "Shrani kot..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to save an existing attachment with a different name."
msgstr "Omogoča shranjevanje obstoječe priloge z drugim imenom."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to copy, cut and paste to and from the clipboard."
msgstr "Omogoča kopiranje, rezanje in lepljenje v in iz odložišča."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected attachment."
msgstr "Izbriše izbrano prilogo."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties..."
msgstr "Lastnosti..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to change an existing attachment."
msgstr "Omogoča spreminjanje obstoječe priloge."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1436 index.docbook:2527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Free/Busy"
msgstr "Prost/zaseden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When adding attendees to your event, you need to know if they are busy or "
"free in that particular time. If the attendees make their free / busy "
"information available, you can view here their schedule before sending the "
"invitations."
msgstr ""
"Ko na svoj dogodek dodajate udeležence, morate vedeti, ali so v tem času "
"zasedeni ali prosti. Če udeleženci dajo na voljo podatke o prostem/"
"zasedenem, si lahko tukaj ogledate njihov urnik, preden pošljete povabila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows the free/busy schedule chart on the right, where each line "
"represents one of the attendees, listed on the left. The marked areas on the "
"chart represent the time already taken by other events, unmarked areas "
"represent time free from other events. You can move the event to a different "
"point in time by dragging it with the mouse, or resize it by moving the "
"edges of the highlighted area with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"To prikazuje grafikon prostih/zasedenih urnikov na desni, kjer vsaka vrstica "
"predstavlja enega od udeležencev, navedenih na levi. Označena območja na "
"grafikonu predstavljajo čas, ki so ga že zavzeli drugi dogodki, neoznačena "
"območja predstavljajo čas brez drugih dogodkov. Dogodek lahko premaknete na "
"drugo časovno točko tako, da ga povlečete z miško, ali pa mu spremenite "
"velikost tako, da z miško premaknete robove označenega območja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The free/busy information is only available if the attendee publishes his "
"free/busy schedule, and if &korganizer; is correctly configured to retrieve "
"it. For more information about configuring &korganizer; to publish and "
"retrieve free/busy information, please check the <xref linkend=\"config\"/>. "
"Double-clicking on an attendee entry in the list will allow you to enter the "
"location of their free/busy information."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o prostem/zasedenem so na voljo le, če udeleženec objavi svoj "
"urnik o prostem/zasedenem in če &korganizer; je pravilno konfiguriran, da ga "
"pridobi. Za več informacij o konfiguraciji &korganizer; za objavo in "
"pridobitev informacij o prostem/zasedenem času preverite <xref linkend="
"\"config\"/>. Če dvakrat kliknete vnos udeleženca na seznamu, boste lahko "
"vnesli lokacijo njegovih informacij o prostem/zasedenem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale"
msgstr "Lestvica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the zoom level on the schedule chart. <guilabel>Hour</guilabel> shows a "
"range of several hours, <guilabel>Day</guilabel> shows a range of a few "
"days, <guilabel>Week</guilabel> shows a range of a few months, and "
"<guilabel>Month</guilabel> shows a range of a few months, while "
"<guilabel>Automatic</guilabel> selects the range most appropriate for the "
"current event or to-do."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi stopnjo povečave na grafikonu urnika. <guilabel>Ura</guilabel> "
"prikazuje obseg nekaj ur, <guilabel>Dan</guilabel> prikazuje obseg nekaj "
"dni, <guilabel>Teden</guilabel> prikazuje obseg nekaj mesecev in <guilabel "
">Mesec</guilabel> prikazuje obseg nekaj mesecev, medtem ko "
"<guilabel>Samodejno</guilabel> izbere obseg, ki je najbolj primeren za "
"trenutni dogodek ali opravilo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Center on Start"
msgstr "Center na začetku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to center the free/busy schedule chart on the start time "
"and day of this event."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da grafikon prostega/zasedenega urnika centrirate na "
"začetni čas in dan tega dogodka."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1477
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pick Date"
msgstr "Izberi datum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to automatically move the event to a date and time when "
"all the attendees are free."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da samodejno premaknete dogodek na datum in uro, ko so "
"vsi udeleženci prosti."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload"
msgstr "Ponovno naloži"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to reload Free/Busy data for all attendees from the "
"corresponding servers."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da ponovno naložite podatke o prostem/zasedenem za vse "
"udeležence z ustreznih strežnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you want to confirm, call off or revert the entered data, choose among "
"the Action Buttons <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ko želite potrditi, preklicati ali razveljaviti vnesene podatke, izberite "
"med akcijskimi gumbi <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, <guibutton>Uporabi</"
"guibutton> in <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manage Templates"
msgstr "Upravljanje predlog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Manage Templates</guibutton> button opens a dialog which "
"enables you to save the current event as a template, so that you can reuse "
"the data entered for future events. As an example you can save a template "
"for a meeting that takes place at the same location and with the same people."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Upravljanje predlog</guibutton> odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam "
"omogoča, da trenutni dogodek shranite kot predlogo, tako da lahko znova "
"uporabite vnesene podatke za prihodnje dogodke. Kot primer lahko shranite "
"predlogo za sestanek, ki poteka na isti lokaciji in z istimi ljudmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button you can use an existing "
"template for your event. Continuing the example in the preceding paragraph "
"you can specify the agenda of the meeting."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> lahko uporabite obstoječo predlogo "
"za svoj dogodek. Z nadaljevanjem primera v prejšnjem odstavku lahko določite "
"dnevni red sestanka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1512
#, no-c-format
msgid "To-dos"
msgstr "Opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The To-do List is a place for you to write down notes to yourself about "
"things that you need to do. To-dos are tasks, that may or may not be "
"scheduled. There are short-term and long-term to-dos. For instance you "
"should go to a hairdresser within a week, and you should sell your old car "
"within a year. You likely do not want a reminder go off at a particular "
"time, you just want to have a list of things that you must do, and dates "
"when they must be finished at the latest (date due)."
msgstr ""
"Seznam opravil je kraj, kjer si lahko zapisujete opombe o stvareh, ki jih "
"morate narediti. Opravila so opravila, ki so lahko načrtovana ali ne. "
"Obstajajo kratkoročna in dolgoročna opravila. Na primer, v enem tednu bi "
"morali iti k frizerju, v enem letu pa prodati svoj stari avto. Verjetno ne "
"želite, da se opomnik sproži ob določenem času, želite le imeti seznam "
"stvari, ki jih morate narediti, in datume, ko morajo biti končane najpozneje "
"(datum zapadlosti)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a new to-do, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New To-do...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A window with "
"five tabs at the bottom will appear."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti novo opravilo, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo opravilo ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže "
"se okno s petimi zavihki na dnu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit To-do dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &korganizer; pogovornega okna za urejanje "
"opravil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit To-do dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Zaslonski posnetek &korganizer; urejevanje seznama opravil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1535
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit To-do dialog</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Posnetek zaslona &korganizer; pogovornega okna za urejanje opravil</"
"para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab shares a lot of options with the <guilabel>Edit Events</guilabel> "
"dialog, but has some additional items for to-dos:"
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek ima veliko skupnih možnosti s pogovornim oknom <guilabel>Urejanje "
"dogodkov</guilabel>, vendar ima nekaj dodatnih elementov za opravila:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completion"
msgstr "Dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a percent completed pull down menu initially set at 0% complete. "
"Later on, you can indicate your progress by adjusting the percent completed "
"in steps of 10%."
msgstr ""
"To je odstotek dokončanega spustnega menija, ki je bil prvotno nastavljen na "
"0 % dokončanega. Kasneje lahko navedete svoj napredek tako, da prilagodite "
"odstotek dokončanega v korakih po 10 %."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Priority"
msgstr "Prioriteta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assign a priority to your to-do. This drop down menu offers priorities from "
"one to nine, one being the highest. Initially to-dos are set to priority "
"five (medium)."
msgstr ""
"Svojim opravilom dodelite prednost. Ta spustni meni ponuja prioritete od ena "
"do devet, pri čemer je ena najvišja. Sprva so opravila nastavljena na "
"prednost pet (srednja)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Required Fields"
msgstr "Zahtevana polja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is an overview of what fields are required and what fields can be empty "
"when entering events and to-dos:"
msgstr ""
"To je pregled, katera polja so obvezna in katera so lahko prazna pri vnosu "
"dogodkov in opravil:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1571
#, no-c-format
msgid "You must fill in the <guilabel>Summary</guilabel> field."
msgstr "Izpolniti morate polje <guilabel>Povzetek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>General</guilabel> Tab may be left completely empty."
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> lahko pustite popolnoma prazen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you set a <guilabel>Reminder</guilabel>, you should also specify the "
"time, and either the sound to be played or the program to be run."
msgstr ""
"Če nastavite <guilabel >Opomnik</guilabel >, morate določiti tudi čas in "
"zvok, ki naj se predvaja, ali program, ki se izvaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Attendees</guilabel> tab may be left completely empty."
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Udeleženci</guilabel> lahko ostane popolnoma prazen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Recurrence</guilabel> tab must only be filled if you select a "
"daily, weekly, monthly or yearly repeat."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Ponovitev</guilabel> mora biti izpolnjen le, če izberete "
"dnevno, tedensko, mesečno ali letno ponovitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Attachments</guilabel> dialog may be left completely empty."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Priloge</guilabel> lahko pustite popolnoma prazno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1589 index.docbook:2493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Group Scheduling"
msgstr "Skupinsko razporejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The group schedule functionality of &korganizer; allows you to organize "
"appointments, meetings and shared to-do items, request responses from "
"attendees and publish items. If you are being invited to an event or to-do, "
"you can reply to it, stating if you will be able to attend, or send a "
"counter proposal, with different arrangements, like a different time or "
"location. You can also publish your free/busy schedule, to let people know "
"when you are available, and request the same information from others."
msgstr ""
"Funkcionalnost skupinskega urnika &korganizer; vam omogoča, da organizirate "
"sestanke, sestanke in elemente opravil v skupni rabi, zahtevate odgovore od "
"udeležencev in objavljate elemente. Če ste povabljeni na dogodek ali "
"opravilo, lahko nanj odgovorite in navedete, ali se ga boste lahko "
"udeležili, ali pošljete nasprotni predlog z drugačnimi dogovori, na primer z "
"drugačnim časom ali lokacijo. Prav tako lahko objavite svoj urnik prostega/"
"zasedenega, da ljudi obvestite, kdaj ste na voljo, in zahtevate iste "
"informacije od drugih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently, &korganizer; schedules events and to-dos using email to transport "
"the data, in a standards based scheme, the IMIP-protocol for group "
"scheduling. Being a standard, IMIP is a used by many other clients too. For "
"example &Microsoft;<application>Outlook</application>, Lotus "
"<application>Notes</application> and Novell <application>Evolution</"
"application>. This means that you can share events with other users using "
"one of these clients. &korganizer; is integrated with &kmail; for receiving, "
"processing, and sending events, event responses, updates, cancellations, "
"&etc; For instance, when you get an invitation in &kmail;, and decide to "
"accept it, by clicking the <guilabel>accept</guilabel> link in the mail "
"body, the event is added to your calendar, and a response to the event's "
"organizer is sent automatically."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno &korganizer; načrtuje dogodke in opravila z uporabo e-pošte za "
"prenos podatkov v shemi, ki temelji na standardih, protokol IMIP za "
"skupinsko razporejanje. Ker je IMIP standard, ga uporabljajo tudi številni "
"drugi odjemalci. Na primer &Microsoft;<application>Outlook</application>, "
"Lotus <application>Notes</application> in Novell <application>Evolution</"
"application>. To pomeni, da lahko z enim od teh odjemalcev delite dogodke z "
"drugimi uporabniki. &korganizer; je integriran z &kmail; za prejemanje, "
"obdelavo in pošiljanje dogodkov, odzivov na dogodke, posodobitev, odpovedi "
"&etc; Na primer, ko prejmete povabilo v &kmail; in se odločite, da ga "
"sprejmete, s klikom na povezavo <guilabel>sprejmi</guilabel> v telesu pošte, "
"se dogodek doda v vaš koledar in odgovor organizatorju dogodka se pošlje "
"samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Use Groupware Communication</guilabel> box in the "
"<link linkend=\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; group scheduling "
"configuration</link>, &korganizer; will handle the group scheduling "
"communication for you. In other words, you will seldom need to use the "
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> menu directly to perform the scheduling actions. "
"For instance, if you <link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">create an event "
"or to-do</link> with attendees, &korganizer; will ask you if you want to "
"send the invitations to the attendees, so you will not need to use the "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Schedule</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Invitation to "
"Attendees</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item later. Also, if you change "
"your status as an attendee for an event you were invited to, it will ask you "
"if you want to send your updated status to the event's organizer, so you "
"will not need to use the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Schedule</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Status Update</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu "
"item later."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Uporabi skupinsko komunikacijo</guilabel> v "
"<link linkend=\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; konfiguracija "
"skupinskega razporejanja</link>, &korganizer; bo namesto vas poskrbel za "
"komunikacijo skupinskega razporejanja. Z drugimi besedami, redko vam bo "
"treba neposredno uporabiti meni <guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> za izvajanje dejanj "
"načrtovanja. Če na primer <link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">ustvarite "
"dogodek ali opravilo</link> z udeleženci, &korganizer; vas bo vprašal, ali "
"želite poslati povabila udeležencem, tako da vam ne bo treba uporabiti "
"menijske postavke <menuchoice> <guimenu>Urnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji "
"povabilo udeležencem</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> pozneje. Poleg tega, če "
"spremenite svoj status udeleženca dogodka, na katerega ste bili povabljeni, "
"vas bo vprašal, ali želite svoje posodobljeno stanje poslati organizatorju "
"dogodka, tako da vam ne bo treba uporabiti <menuchoice> <guimenu>Urnik </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji posodobitev stanja</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"element menija pozneje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publishing an Event, To-do or Journal Entry"
msgstr "Objava dogodka, opravila ali vnosa v dnevnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you simply want to send an event, to-do or journal entry, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu><guimenuitem>Publish Item "
"Information...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, when the item is "
"selected. Then a dialog appears, asking you the email addresses which will "
"receive the event or to-do. The item will be sent by email, in the iCalendar "
"format."
msgstr ""
"Če preprosto želite poslati dogodek, opravilo ali vnos v dnevnik, izberite "
"element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu><guimenuitem>Objavi "
"informacije o predmetu ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ko element je izbran. "
"Nato se prikaže pogovorno okno, ki vas vpraša za e-poštne naslove, na katere "
"boste prejeli dogodek ali opravilo. Predmet bo poslan po e-pošti v formatu "
"iCalendar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that you can use this action to email any item to anyone, not "
"just to the item's attendees. In fact, you can publish an item with no "
"attendees at all, as publishing does not request an answer from the "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko to dejanje uporabite za pošiljanje katerega koli "
"predmeta po e-pošti komur koli, ne le udeležencem predmeta. Pravzaprav lahko "
"objavite element brez udeležencev, saj objava ne zahteva odgovora "
"udeležencev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An example: you are playing in a band and, from time to time, you give live "
"concerts. To notify your fans about the concerts, you maintain a mailing "
"list. If you use &korganizer; to organize your concert dates, you can just "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Publish Item "
"Information...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, put in the address of "
"the mailing list and the event gets sent. Mailing list subscribers who use "
"&korganizer; get the concert date automatically inserted in their calendar."
msgstr ""
"Primer: igrate v skupini in občasno koncertirate v živo. Če želite svoje "
"oboževalce obveščati o koncertih, vzdržujete poštni seznam. Če uporabljate "
"&korganizer; če želite organizirati svoje koncertne datume, lahko preprosto "
"izberete element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Objavi informacije o predmetu ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"vnesete naslov poštnega seznama in dogodek bo poslan. Naročniki na poštni "
"seznam, ki uporabljajo &korganizer; da se datum koncerta samodejno vstavi v "
"njihov koledar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Publishing an event as described above will only inform the receiver about "
"the event, but not give her the option to ask for attendance. Use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send as iCalendar...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> if you want to provide that option instead."
msgstr ""
"Objava dogodka, kot je opisano zgoraj, bo prejemnika le obvestila o dogodku, "
"ne pa ji dala možnosti, da zaprosi za udeležbo. Uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Urnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji kot iCalendar ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, če želite ponuditi to možnost namesto tega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acting as Organizer in Group Scheduling"
msgstr "Deluje kot organizator pri skupinskem razporejanju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create <link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">an event</link> or "
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">a to-do</link>, and <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events-attendees\">add attendees to it</link>, you are "
"acting as the event organizer. To add attendees, use the <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events-attendees\"> attendee tab</link>, in the "
"<guilabel>Edit Event</guilabel>, or <guilabel>Edit To-do</guilabel> dialog. "
"In the <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Agenda view</link>, a little icon "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"organizer.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Organizer Icon</phrase> "
"</textobject> </inlinemediaobject> is placed in the event, if you are the "
"organizer of a group scheduling event."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite <link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">dogodek</link> ali <link "
"linkend=\"entering-data-to-do\">opravilo</link> in <link linkend=\"entering-"
"data-events-attendees\">dodajte udeležence</link>, nastopate kot organizator "
"dogodka. Če želite dodati udeležence, uporabite <link linkend=\"entering-"
"data-events-attendees\"> zavihek udeleženec</link> v <guilabel>Urejanje "
"dogodka</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Urejanje opravil</guilabel > dialog. V "
"<link linkend=\"agenda-view\">pogledu dnevnega reda</link> majhna ikona "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"organizer.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject > <phrase>Ikona organizatorja</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> je postavljena v dogodek, če ste "
"organizator dogodka s skupinskim razporedom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The organizer is responsible for sending the invitations, collecting the "
"attendees responses, and for keeping the data of the event or to-do up to "
"date for all people involved."
msgstr ""
"Organizator je odgovoren za pošiljanje vabil, zbiranje odgovorov udeležencev "
"in za ažurnost podatkov o dogodku ali opravilih za vse udeležene osebe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending Invitations and Processing Responses"
msgstr "Pošiljanje povabil in obdelava odgovorov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To organize an event or to-do, <link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">create "
"it</link> in &korganizer; and add all the people that should attend using "
"the attendees tab. &korganizer; can send invitations to the attendees, "
"either automatically (depending on <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"groupscheduling\">&korganizer; group scheduling configuration</link>), or by "
"selecting the event or to-do and choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Invitation to Attendees</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"menu item. The attendees get an email containing all the relevant "
"information for the event or to-do. They can respond to the meeting proposal "
"by accepting or rejecting it or by making a counter proposal. They can also "
"delegate or forward the invitation. All this information is sent to you by "
"email again and, if you have configured &kmail; appropriately, the attendees "
"responses are automatically inserted in your calendar. If there are "
"additional attendees willing to participate (e.g. by accepting a forwarded "
"invitation) you will be asked to accept the new attendees."
msgstr ""
"Če želite organizirati dogodek ali opravilo, <link linkend=\"entering-data-"
"events\">ga ustvarite</link> v &korganizer; in dodajte vse ljudi, ki bi se "
"morali udeležiti, z uporabo zavihka udeležencev. &korganizer; lahko pošlje "
"vabila udeležencem, bodisi samodejno (odvisno od <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"groupscheduling\">&korganizer; konfiguracije skupinskega razporejanja</"
"link>) ali tako, da izbere dogodek ali opravilo in izbere <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji povabilo udeležencem</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> element menija. Udeleženci prejmejo e-pošto z "
"vsemi relevantnimi informacijami za dogodek ali opravilo. Na predlog "
"sestanka se lahko odzovejo tako, da ga sprejmejo ali zavrnejo ali dajo "
"nasprotni predlog. Vabilo lahko tudi prenesejo ali posredujejo. Vse te "
"informacije vam ponovno pošljemo po e-pošti in, če ste konfigurirali &kmail; "
"ustrezno se odgovori udeležencev samodejno vstavijo v vaš koledar. Če "
"obstajajo dodatni udeleženci, ki želijo sodelovati (npr. s sprejetjem "
"posredovanega povabila), boste pozvani, da sprejmete nove udeležence."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancelling an Event or To-do"
msgstr "Preklic dogodka ali opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To cancel an event or to-do you have to be the organizer. If you checked the "
"<guilabel>Use Groupware Communication</guilabel> box in the <link linkend="
"\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; group scheduling configuration</"
"link>, just delete the item, and &korganizer; will ask you to send the "
"cancellation. If not, simply select the item, and choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send Cancellation to "
"Attendees</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpovedati dogodek ali opravilo, morate biti organizator. Če ste "
"označili polje <guilabel>Uporabi skupinsko komunikacijo</guilabel> v <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; konfiguracija "
"skupinskega razporejanja</link>, samo izbrišite element in &korganizer; vas "
"bo prosil, da pošljete preklic. Če ne, preprosto izberite element in "
"izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pošlji preklic udeležencem</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action will send a cancel-message to all attendees, so they can remove "
"the item from their calendars too."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje bo poslalo sporočilo o preklicu vsem udeležencem, tako da lahko "
"odstranijo element tudi iz svojih koledarjev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acting as the Attendee"
msgstr "Deluje kot udeleženec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you get an email with an invitation and accept it, the event or to-do "
"is added to your calendar. If it is an event, a little icon "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"meeting-attending.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Attendee Icon</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> is placed in the event in the "
"<link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Agenda view</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko prejmete e-poštno sporočilo s povabilom in ga sprejmete, se dogodek ali "
"opravilo doda v vaš koledar. Če gre za dogodek, majhna ikona "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"meeting-attending.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Ikona udeleženca</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> je postavljen v dogodek v <link "
"linkend=\"agenda-view\">pogledu dnevnega reda</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Answering an Invitation"
msgstr "Odgovor na povabilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have an invitation in your &kmail; inbox you can either press "
"<guibutton>Reject</guibutton> to ignore the request, or press "
"<guibutton>Accept</guibutton> or <guibutton>Accept Cond.</guibutton>. The "
"last two actions will insert the item into your calendar. In any case, "
"&kmail; will send your response to the organizer automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če imate povabilo v &kmail; Prejeto lahko pritisnete <guibutton>Zavrni</"
"guibutton>, da prezrete zahtevo, ali pritisnete <guibutton>Sprejmi</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>Sprejmi pogoj</guibutton>. Zadnji dve dejanji "
"bosta element vstavili v vaš koledar. V vsakem primeru &kmail; bo vaš "
"odgovor samodejno poslal organizatorju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also <guibutton>Delegate</guibutton> or <guibutton>Forward</"
"guibutton> the invitation. When delegating, you can suggest another person "
"as your proxy. Using <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> you can forward the "
"invitation to one or more people not yet invited. When the receiver of the "
"delegation or forward accepts the invitation, the organizer will be asked to "
"approve the new attendee."
msgstr ""
"Povabilo lahko tudi <guibutton>pooblastite</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>posredujete</guibutton>. Pri delegiranju lahko predlagate drugo "
"osebo kot pooblaščenca. Z <guibutton>Posreduj</guibutton> lahko povabilo "
"posredujete eni ali več osebam, ki še niso povabljene. Ko sprejemnik "
"delegacije ali posrednik sprejme povabilo, bo organizator pozvan, da odobri "
"novega udeleženca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If for any reason you changed your mind, edit your status in the item's "
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-events-attendees\">attendee tab</link>. If you "
"checked the <guilabel>Use Groupware Communication</guilabel> box in the "
"<link linkend=\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; group scheduling "
"configuration</link>, &korganizer; will ask you to send an email updating "
"your attendee status. If not, choose the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Schedule</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Status Update</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu "
"item to send your status update."
msgstr ""
"Če ste si iz kakršnega koli razloga premislili, uredite svoje stanje na "
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-events-attendees\">zavihku udeležencev</link> "
"predmeta. Če ste označili polje <guilabel>Uporabi skupinsko komunikacijo</"
"guilabel> v <link linkend=\"config-main-groupscheduling\">&korganizer; "
"konfiguracija skupinskega razporejanja</link>, &korganizer; vas bo prosil, "
"da pošljete e-poštno sporočilo s posodobitvijo statusa udeleženca. Če ne, "
"izberite element menija <menuchoice> <guimenu>Razpored</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji posodobitev stanja</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, "
"da pošljete posodobitev stanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1781
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending an Alternative Proposal"
msgstr "Pošiljanje alternativnega predloga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are not satisfied with some of the characteristics of the event or to-"
"do you got invited to, and want to send a counter proposal to the organizer "
"(for instance an alternative location or time), just edit the item and send "
"it back as your proposal, by selecting the item and choosing the "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Schedule</guimenu><guimenuitem>Request Change</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če niste zadovoljni z nekaterimi značilnostmi dogodka ali opravila, na "
"katerega ste bili povabljeni, in želite poslati nasprotni predlog "
"organizatorju (na primer alternativna lokacija ali čas), preprosto uredite "
"element in ga pošljite nazaj kot vaš predlog, tako da izberete postavko in "
"izberete menijsko postavko <menuchoice> <guimenu>Urnik</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zahtevaj spremembo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The organizer of the event will get your proposal by email, and will be able "
"to accept it or decline."
msgstr ""
"Organizator dogodka bo vašo ponudbo prejel po elektronski pošti in jo bo "
"lahko sprejel ali zavrnil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Requesting the Latest Version of an Event or To-do"
msgstr "Zahtevanje najnovejše različice dogodka ali opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To request the latest version of an event or to-do, select the item, and "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Request "
"Update</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. The organizer should then send "
"you back the latest version of the item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zahtevati najnovejšo različico dogodka ali opravila, izberite "
"element in izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zahtevaj posodobitev</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Organizator "
"vam mora nato poslati nazaj najnovejšo različico predmeta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid "Free Busy information"
msgstr "Brezplačne informacije o zasedenosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1810 index.docbook:2529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The free/busy information represents an availability schedule. By presenting "
"the intervals when one already has previous commitments, others can avoid "
"arranging appointments for these periods. Note that only the times are "
"published, not the events, reasons or attendees."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o prostem/zasedenem času predstavljajo razpored "
"razpoložljivosti. S predstavitvijo intervalov, ko ima nekdo že predhodne "
"obveznosti, se lahko drugi izognejo dogovarjanju za te termine. Upoštevajte, "
"da so objavljeni samo časi, ne pa dogodki, razlogi ali udeleženci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1815 index.docbook:2534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; supports publishing and retrieving free/busy information, "
"either manually or automatically."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; podpira objavljanje in pridobivanje informacij o prostem/"
"zasedenem, ročno ali samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To email your free/busy information, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mail Free Busy "
"Information...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Enter the email "
"addresses you want to send the information to in the dialog and press "
"<guilabel>OK</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite podatke o prosti/zasedenosti poslati po e-pošti, izberite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji "
"informacije o prosti/zasedenosti ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V pogovorno "
"okno vnesite e-poštne naslove, na katere želite poslati podatke, in "
"pritisnite <guilabel>V redu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Groupware servers usually have a standard location for uploading your free "
"busy information, so that other users can access your data, and you can "
"access other user's free busy schedule. You can configure &korganizer; to "
"upload and download free busy information automatically, using the <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-free-busy\">Free Busy preferences</link>, in the "
"&korganizer; <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Strežniki skupinske opreme imajo običajno standardno lokacijo za nalaganje "
"vaših informacij o zasedenosti, tako da lahko drugi uporabniki dostopajo do "
"vaših podatkov, vi pa lahko dostopate do urnika zasedenosti drugih "
"uporabnikov. Konfigurirate lahko &korganizer; za samodejno nalaganje in "
"prenašanje informacij o zasedenosti z uporabo <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"free-busy\">nastavitev prostega zasedenosti</link> v &korganizer; "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel> pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To upload your free/busy information to the server set in &korganizer; "
"preferences, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Upload Free Busy Information</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Za nalaganje informacij o prostem/zasedenem strežniku, nastavljenem v "
"&korganizer; nastavitve, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži informacije o "
"prosti zasedenosti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Primeri"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering a New Group Event"
msgstr "Vstop v nov skupinski dogodek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this example, you'll enter an event. You need to arrange a meeting on "
"<emphasis>the next Monday</emphasis> regarding launch of your new Product. "
"Your boss <emphasis>Joan Holden</emphasis> will be the event chairwoman "
"<emphasis>owner</emphasis>, and you, Jack Smith, will be the event "
"<emphasis>organizer</emphasis>. There will be two more <emphasis>attendees</"
"emphasis> (participants): <emphasis>Peter Krzinski</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>Kirsten Friese</emphasis>. Joan gave you the program of the "
"meeting. The appointment will start at <emphasis>12 noon</emphasis> and end "
"at <emphasis>1 pm</emphasis>. The same appointment should be scheduled "
"<emphasis>(recurred)</emphasis> each Monday."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru boste vnesli dogodek. Za <emphasis>naslednji ponedeljek</"
"emphasis> se morate dogovoriti za sestanek glede lansiranja vašega novega "
"izdelka. Vaša šefica <emphasis>Joan Holden</emphasis> bo predsednica dogodka "
"<emphasis>lastnik</emphasis>, vi, Jack Smith, pa boste "
"<emphasis>organizator</emphasis> dogodka. Prisotna bosta še dva "
"<emphasis>udeleženca</emphasis> (udeleženca): <emphasis>Peter Krzinski</"
"emphasis> in <emphasis>Kirsten Friese</emphasis>. Joan vam je dala program "
"srečanja. Sestanek se bo začel ob <emphasis>12h</emphasis> in končal ob "
"<emphasis>13h</emphasis>. Isti termin bi moral biti načrtovan "
"<emphasis>(ponavlja se)</emphasis> vsak ponedeljek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Date Navigator, go to the next Monday."
msgstr "Z uporabo Krmarja po datumih pojdite na naslednji ponedeljek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Event...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or select the area between <emphasis>12 noon</"
"emphasis> and end at<emphasis>1 pm</emphasis>, and start typing the event "
"summary."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov dogodek ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali izberite območje med <emphasis>12. uro</"
"emphasis> in koncem ob <emphasis> 13h</emphasis> in začnite tipkati povzetek "
"dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a suitable summary. It's important to choose the right brief "
"description, because it appears in many places. We suggest that you enter "
"<userinput>Product launch event</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ustrezen povzetek. Pomembno je izbrati pravi kratek opis, saj se "
"pojavlja marsikje. Predlagamo, da vnesete <userinput>Dogodek lansiranja "
"izdelka</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the detailed event program into the largest rectangle area. For the "
"sake of this simple example, enter <userinput>Introduction, The Plan, "
"Conclusion</userinput> on three separate lines."
msgstr ""
"V največje pravokotno območje vnesite podroben program dogodka. Zaradi tega "
"preprostega primera vnesite <userinput>Uvod, Načrt, Zaključek</userinput> v "
"tri ločene vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <guilabel>Reminder</guilabel> tab. Set the reminder time to 15 "
"minutes, just long enough to brew a cup of tea prior to the meeting start."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Opomnik</guilabel>. Nastavite čas opomnika na "
"15 minut, ravno toliko, da skuhate skodelico čaja pred začetkom sestanka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab. Select <guilabel>Appointment</"
"guilabel> from the <guilabel>Manage Tags</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>. V pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Upravljanje oznak</guilabel> izberite <guilabel>Sestanek</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <guilabel>Recurrence</guilabel> tab and select the "
"<guilabel>Weekly</guilabel> repeats."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Ponavljanje</guilabel> in izberite "
"<guilabel>Tedenska</guilabel> ponavljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most work has been done for you automatically. &korganizer; defaults to "
"recurring weekly. Also note that <guilabel>Ends:</guilabel> <guilabel>never</"
"guilabel> is chosen. This means that this event will be repeated each Monday "
"(starting, of course, on Monday August 30, 2010) until the end of time (that "
"is, until you delete it)."
msgstr ""
"Večina dela je bila namesto vas opravljena samodejno. &korganizer; privzeto "
"se ponavlja tedensko. Upoštevajte tudi, da je izbrano <guilabel>Konča se:</"
"guilabel> <guilabel>nikoli</guilabel>. To pomeni, da se bo ta dogodek "
"ponavljal vsak ponedeljek (začenši seveda s ponedeljkom, 30. avgusta 2010) "
"do konca časa (to je, dokler ga ne izbrišete)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since everything is all right here, click the <guilabel>Attendees</guilabel> "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Ker je tukaj vse v redu, kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Udeleženci</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1890
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guilabel>Attendees</guilabel> tab you should do the following:"
msgstr "Na zavihku <guilabel>Udeleženci</guilabel> storite naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will see that you are the organizer of the event."
msgstr "Videli boste, da ste organizator dogodka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the first input field enter the email in the <userinput>Name &#060;"
"email&#062;</userinput> format. In our example, enter <userinput>Joan Holden "
"&#060;jholden@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"V prvo vnosno polje vnesite e-pošto v obliki <userinput>Ime &#060;e-"
"pošta&#062;</userinput>. V našem primeru vnesite <userinput>Joan Holden "
"&#060;jholden@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the attendees are already in your &kde; address book, instead of typing "
"the names and emails, you can press the <guibutton>Select Attendees...</"
"guibutton> button to add them."
msgstr ""
"Če so udeleženci že v vašem &kde; imenik, namesto da vnašate imena in e-"
"poštne naslove, lahko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Izberi udeležence...</"
"guibutton>, da jih dodate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose <emphasis>Chair</emphasis> as the role."
msgstr "Izberite <emphasis>Predsednika</emphasis> kot vlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the next input field enter <userinput>Peter Krzinski &#060;"
"pkrzinski@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"V naslednje polje za vnos vnesite <userinput>Peter Krzinski &#060;"
"pkrzinski@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the next input field enter <userinput>Kirsten Friese &#060;"
"kfriese@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"V naslednje polje za vnos vnesite <userinput>Kirsten Friese &#060;"
"kfriese@thiscompany.com&#062;</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have configured &korganizer; to use groupware communication, you will "
"be asked if you want to send an email to the attendees, with details of the "
"event and asking for a response if the <guilabel>Request response</guilabel> "
"box from the <guilabel>Attendees</guilabel> tab is checked. Else, you can "
"send the invitations choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Send Invitation to Attendees</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Če ste konfigurirali &korganizer; če želite uporabljati skupinsko "
"komunikacijo, boste pozvani, ali želite poslati e-pošto udeležencem s "
"podrobnostmi o dogodku in zahtevo za odgovor, če polje <guilabel>Zahtevaj "
"odgovor</guilabel> od <guilabel>Udeleženci</guilabel> zavihek je označen. "
"Sicer pa lahko povabila pošljete tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji povabilo "
"udeležencem</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Review the event setup by clicking on the tabs. If you are satisfied, click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte nastavitev dogodka s klikom na zavihke. Če ste zadovoljni, "
"kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Congratulations, you've scheduled your first event!"
msgstr "Čestitamo, načrtovali ste svoj prvi dogodek!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1936
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer; Configuration"
msgstr "&korganizer; Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change &korganizer;'s look and behavior, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &korganizer;..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. You can get more information about "
"all the configure options and possibilities in <xref linkend=\"config-main\"/"
">."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti videz in delovanje &korganizer;, izberite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&korganizer;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Več informacij o vseh "
"konfiguracijskih možnostih in možnostih najdete v <xref linkend=\"config-main"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To customize the set of tools available on the bar, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars... </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and read the Section <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/config.html#toolbars\">Customizing Toolbars</ulink> in the "
"&kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi nabor orodij, ki so na voljo v vrstici, izberite "
"menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice ... </guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in preberite razdelek <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config."
"html#toolbars\">Prilagajanje orodnih vrstic</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Localization information like date and time formats can be configured from "
"&systemsettings; within the modules <guilabel>Language</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Formats</guilabel>. These control modules can be accessed from "
"within &korganizer;: just choose the <menuchoice><guimenu> Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Date &amp; Time...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"menu item. &korganizer; has to be restarted for changes done in "
"&systemsettings; to take effect."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o lokalizaciji, kot so formati datuma in časa, je mogoče "
"konfigurirati v &systemsettings; znotraj modulov <guilabel>Jezik</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Oblike</guilabel>. Do teh nadzornih modulov lahko dostopate "
"znotraj &korganizer;: samo izberite <menuchoice><guimenu> Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj datum &amp; Čas ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menijski element. &korganizer; je treba znova zagnati zaradi "
"sprememb v &systemsettings; da začne veljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure where &korganizer; stores and retrieves calendar events, "
"journal entries and to-dos, (in local files, groupware servers &etc;), "
"please check <xref linkend=\"managing-resources\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati, kje &korganizer; shranjuje in pridobiva dogodke v "
"koledarju, vnose v dnevnik in opravila (v lokalnih datotekah, strežnikih "
"skupinske programske opreme &etc;), preverite <xref linkend=\"managing-"
"resources\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1963
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer; Main Configuration"
msgstr "&korganizer; Glavna konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options dialog lets you configure a number of different areas of "
"&korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno z možnostmi vam omogoča, da konfigurirate več različnih "
"področij &korganizer;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1969
#, no-c-format
msgid "General page"
msgstr "Splošna stran"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Personal tab"
msgstr "Osebni zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The personal options relate to your personal identity, and other "
"miscellaneous things that do not fall under any of the other general "
"categories."
msgstr ""
"Osebne možnosti se nanašajo na vašo osebno identiteto in druge stvari, ki ne "
"spadajo v nobeno drugo splošno kategorijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full name"
msgstr "Polno ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Full name</guilabel> is initially set to <quote>Anonymous</quote> "
"with an email address of <quote>nobody@nowhere</quote>. You can change your "
"name by directly entering it here. This name will be displayed by default as "
"<guilabel>Organizer</guilabel> in to-dos and Events."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Polno ime</guilabel> je prvotno nastavljeno na <quote>Anonimno</"
"quote> z e-poštnim naslovom <quote>nobody@nowhere</quote>. Svoje ime lahko "
"spremenite tako, da ga neposredno vnesete tukaj. To ime bo privzeto "
"prikazano kot <guilabel>Organizator</guilabel> v opravilih in dogodkih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1990
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email address"
msgstr "E-poštni naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Email address</guilabel> will be used to identify the owner of the "
"calendar. When another person opens your calendar or events, he/she will not "
"be able to modify it because it will be read-only."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>E-poštni naslov</guilabel> bo uporabljen za identifikacijo "
"lastnika koledarja. Ko druga oseba odpre vaš koledar ali dogodke, jih ne bo "
"mogla spreminjati, ker bo samo za branje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Email Attachment Method"
msgstr "Privzeta metoda e-poštne priloge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to select the way an email is attached to an event. "
"You can attach an email as the complete email including attachments, the "
"email excluding attachments or only a link to the email."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da izberete način, kako je e-poštno sporočilo "
"priloženo dogodku. E-poštno sporočilo lahko priložite kot celotno e-poštno "
"sporočilo s prilogami, e-poštno sporočilo brez prilog ali samo povezavo do e-"
"poštnega sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that attaching an email without attachments might invalidate its "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko pripenjanje e-poštnega sporočila brez prilog "
"razveljavi njegov podpis."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2009
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save tab"
msgstr "Shrani zavihek"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2014
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirm deletes"
msgstr "Potrdi brisanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you check <guilabel>Confirm deletes</guilabel> box, &korganizer; will "
"ask you to confirm each deletion. If this is not checked, &korganizer; will "
"not ask before deleting events."
msgstr ""
"Ko potrdite polje <guilabel>Potrdi brisanje</guilabel>, &korganizer; vas bo "
"prosil za potrditev vsakega izbrisa. Če to ni označeno, &korganizer; ne bo "
"vprašal pred brisanjem dogodkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2022
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Events, To-dos and Journal Entries Should"
msgstr "Novi dogodki, opravila in vnosi v dnevnik bi morali"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you choose between adding new items to the default calendar "
"or making &korganizer; ask you which calendar should be used to save each "
"new item."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča izbiro med dodajanjem novih elementov v privzeti "
"koledar ali ustvarjanjem &korganizer; vas vpraša, kateri koledar je treba "
"uporabiti za shranjevanje vsakega novega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kolab2 server specificity: It is recommended to choose <guilabel>Be asked "
"which calendar to use</guilabel>, if you intend to use the shared folder "
"functionality of the <guilabel>Kolab</guilabel> server. This will allow you "
"to keep control of which information is available only to you, and which "
"information is published in the shared folders."
msgstr ""
"Specifičnost strežnika Kolab2: Priporočljivo je, da izberete "
"<guilabel>Vprašanje, kateri koledar naj uporabi</guilabel>, če nameravate "
"uporabiti funkcijo skupne mape strežnika <guilabel>Kolab</guilabel>. To vam "
"bo omogočilo nadzor nad tem, katere informacije so na voljo samo vam in "
"katere informacije so objavljene v mapah v skupni rabi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time and Date"
msgstr "Čas in datum"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regional tab"
msgstr "Regionalni zavihek"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2053
#, no-c-format
msgid "Day begins at"
msgstr "Dan se začne ob"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the time you start your day from the drop down list. It could be the "
"time when you usually get up, or the time when you start working. This "
"setting does not prevent you from adding or viewing items before this time, "
"it just sets the time that will be displayed by default on the top of the "
"calendar view. Use the scrollbar to display earlier or later events in the "
"Agenda view."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu izberite uro, ko začnete dan. Lahko je čas, ko običajno "
"vstanete, ali čas, ko začnete delati. Ta nastavitev vam ne preprečuje "
"dodajanja ali ogledovanja elementov pred tem časom, le nastavi čas, ki bo "
"privzeto prikazan na vrhu pogleda koledarja. Uporabite drsni trak za prikaz "
"prejšnjih ali poznejših dogodkov v pogledu dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2063
#, no-c-format
msgid "Holidays"
msgstr "Prazniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select your country from the drop down list, or if it is not listed, select "
"<guilabel>(None)</guilabel>. If your country is selected, &korganizer; will "
"recognize and display its important dates and holidays in the calendar view."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu izberite svojo državo ali, če je ni na seznamu, izberite "
"<guilabel>(Brez)</guilabel>. Če je izbrana vaša država, &korganizer; "
"prepozna in prikaže svoje pomembne datume in praznike v pogledu koledarja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weekly Schedule"
msgstr "Tedenski razpored"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options <guilabel>Daily starting hour</guilabel> and <guilabel>Daily "
"ending hour</guilabel> let you specify when your typical day starts and when "
"it ends. &korganizer; sets the hours apart by marking them with a different "
"color from the hours outside of your regular routine and from holidays."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostma <guilabel>Dnevna začetna ura</guilabel> in <guilabel>Dnevna "
"končna ura</guilabel> lahko določite, kdaj se vaš običajni dan začne in kdaj "
"konča. &korganizer; loči ure tako, da jih označi z drugačno barvo od ur "
"izven vaše običajne rutine in od počitnic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, you have check boxes beside each day of the week. Check the "
"week days that are part of your regular schedule, typically excluding "
"weekends. &korganizer; will mark hours that are part of your daily schedule "
"(perhaps your weekly work schedule) differently from hours outside of your "
"regular schedule. Checking <guilabel>Exclude holidays</guilabel> prevents "
"&korganizer; from marking regular schedule (or work) hours for the holiday "
"days in the region defined in the <guilabel>Use holiday region</guilabel> "
"drop down above."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega imate poleg vsakega dne v tednu potrditvena polja. Preverite "
"dneve v tednu, ki so del vašega rednega urnika, običajno brez koncev tedna. "
"&korganizer; bo ure, ki so del vašega dnevnega urnika (morda vašega "
"tedenskega delovnega urnika), označil drugače kot ure izven vašega rednega "
"razporeda. Preverjanje <guilabel>Izključi praznike</guilabel> prepreči "
"&korganizer; od označevanja rednega urnika (ali delovnega časa) za praznične "
"dni v regiji, določeni v zgornjem spustnem meniju <guilabel>Uporabi "
"počitniško regijo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2087
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weekly Start Day"
msgstr "Tedenski začetni dan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2088
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the first day of each week. Normally, you can ignore this since it is "
"set in your locale."
msgstr ""
"Izberite prvi dan vsakega tedna. Običajno lahko to prezrete, ker je "
"nastavljeno v vašem jeziku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2096
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Values tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Privzete vrednosti"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default appointment time"
msgstr "Privzeti čas sestanka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the default start time for events from the drop down list. When you "
"choose <link linkend=\"menu-actions-new-event\">New Event</link> from the "
"<link linkend=\"entering-data-events\">Actions Menu</link>, or create an "
"event in some other manner such that &korganizer; cannot guess when you "
"would like your event to start, &korganizer; will put this hour in the start "
"time editor as the default value."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu izberite privzeti začetni čas za dogodke. Ko izberete "
"<link linkend=\"menu-actions-new-event\">Nov dogodek</link> v <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events\">meniju dejanj</link> ali ustvarite dogodek v na "
"drug način, tako da &korganizer; ne more uganiti, kdaj želite, da se vaš "
"dogodek začne, &korganizer; bo to uro postavil v urejevalnik začetnega časa "
"kot privzeto vrednost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default duration of new appointment (HH:MM):"
msgstr "Privzeto trajanje novega sestanka (HH:MM):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the default duration for events using the spin box. When you choose "
"<link linkend=\"menu-actions-new-event\">New Event</link> from the <link "
"linkend=\"entering-data-events\">Actions Menu</link>, or create an event in "
"some other manner such that &korganizer; cannot guess its duration, "
"&korganizer; will use this as the default value."
msgstr ""
"Z vrtilnim poljem izberite privzeto trajanje dogodkov. Ko izberete <link "
"linkend=\"menu-actions-new-event\">Nov dogodek</link> v <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events\">meniju dejanj</link> ali ustvarite dogodek v na "
"drug način, tako da &korganizer; ne more uganiti njegovega trajanja, "
"&korganizer; bo to uporabil kot privzeto vrednost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reminders"
msgstr "Opomniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a <guilabel>Default reminder time</guilabel> to determine how long "
"before the actual event's scheduled time the reminder will activate."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Privzeti čas opomnika</guilabel>, da določite, kako dolgo "
"pred načrtovanim časom dejanskega dogodka se bo opomnik aktiviral."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set a file to be used as the default sound file for new reminders. You can "
"always specify another file in the Advanced Reminder accessible from the "
"event or to-do editors."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite datoteko, ki bo uporabljena kot privzeta zvočna datoteka za nove "
"opomnike. Vedno lahko določite drugo datoteko v naprednem opomniku, ki je "
"dostopen iz urejevalnikov dogodkov ali opravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the next two boxes if you want to enable reminders for all newly "
"created events or to-dos. You can always turn-off the reminders in the "
"editor dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite naslednji dve polji, če želite omogočiti opomnike za vse novo "
"ustvarjene dogodke ali opravila. Opomnike lahko kadar koli izklopite v "
"pogovornih oknih urejevalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Views"
msgstr "Ogledi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2139
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options let you configure &korganizer; views:"
msgstr "Te možnosti vam omogočajo konfiguracijo &korganizer; pogledi:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2142
#, no-c-format
msgid "General tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Splošno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next x days:"
msgstr "Naslednjih x dni:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to change the number of days shown by the "
"<guimenu>Next x Days</guimenu> menu item in the <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da spremenite število dni, ki jih prikaže menijska "
"postavka <guimenu>Naslednjih x dni</guimenu> v meniju <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable tooltips for displaying summaries"
msgstr "Omogoči opise orodij za prikaz povzetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your summary for an event is longer than would fit in the current View, "
"the remaining characters are not displayed. Check <guilabel>Enable tooltips "
"for displaying summaries</guilabel> if you want the full summary displayed "
"when hovering the mouse pointer over the appointment for a few seconds."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaš povzetek za dogodek daljši, kot bi ustrezal trenutnemu pogledu, "
"preostali znaki niso prikazani. Označite <guilabel>Omogoči opise orodij za "
"prikaz povzetkov</guilabel>, če želite, da se prikaže celoten povzetek, ko "
"miškin kazalec za nekaj sekund podržite nad sestankom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2161
#, no-c-format
msgid "To-dos use tag colors"
msgstr "Opravila uporabljajo barve oznak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box so that to-dos will use tag colors and not colors specific to "
"their due, due today or overdue state."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, da bodo opravila uporabljala barve oznak in ne barv, ki "
"so značilne za njihov rok, rok danes ali zapadlost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"description-view\">Date Navigator</link> options:"
msgstr ""
"Možnosti <link linkend=\"description-view\">Navigatorja po datumih</link>:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show items that recur daily"
msgstr "Pokaži elemente, ki se ponavljajo vsak dan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Show items that recur daily</guilabel> box is checked, the "
"days containing daily recurring events are shown in bold typeface in the "
"Date Navigator."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje <guilabel>Pokaži elemente, ki se ponavljajo vsak dan</guilabel> "
"označeno, so dnevi, ki vsebujejo vsakodnevne ponavljajoče se dogodke, "
"prikazani s krepko pisavo v Krmarju po datumih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show items that recur weekly"
msgstr "Prikaži elemente, ki se ponavljajo tedensko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Show items that recur weekly</guilabel> box is checked, the "
"days containing weekly recurring events are shown in bold typeface in the "
"Date Navigator."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje <guilabel>Prikaži elemente, ki se tedensko ponavljajo</guilabel> "
"označeno, so dnevi, ki vsebujejo tedensko ponavljajoče se dogodke, prikazani "
"s krepko pisavo v Krmarju po datumih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show to-dos instead of events when in Todo View"
msgstr "Pokaži opravila namesto dogodkov v pogledu opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to show the days containing to-dos in bold typeface in the "
"Date Navigator when in To-do view."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite to polje, če želite prikazati dneve, ki vsebujejo opravila, s "
"krepko pisavo v Krmarju po datumih, ko ste v pogledu opravil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show journals instead of events when in Journal View"
msgstr "Pokaži dnevnike namesto dogodkov v pogledu dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to show the days containing journals in bold typeface in the "
"Date Navigator when in Journal view."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite prikazati dneve, ki vsebujejo dnevnike, s "
"krepko pisavo v Krmarju po datumih, ko ste v pogledu dnevnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Week numbers select a work week when in work week mode"
msgstr "Številke tednov izberejo delovni teden v načinu delovnega tedna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Week numbers select a work week when in work week mode</"
"guilabel> box is checked, clicking on the week numbers along the side of the "
"Date Navigator will navigate through work weeks rather than through normal 7-"
"day weeks."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje <guilabel>Številke tednov izberejo delovni teden v načinu "
"delovnega tedna</guilabel> potrjeno, boste s klikom na številke tednov ob "
"strani Krmarja po datumih krmarili po delovnih tednih namesto po običajnih 7-"
"dnevnih tednih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Agenda View tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pogled dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Agenda View</link> options:"
msgstr "Možnosti <link linkend=\"agenda-view\">Pogleda dnevnega reda</link>:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hour size:"
msgstr "Velikost ure:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using this you can control the height of the rows in the Agenda view."
msgstr "S tem lahko nadzirate višino vrstic v pogledu dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show icons in agenda view items"
msgstr "Pokaži ikone v točkah pogleda dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to display icons (reminder, recursion &etc;) in Agenda view "
"items"
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite prikazati ikone (opomnik, rekurzija &etc;) v "
"elementih pogleda dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw bold horizontal grid lines for the even hours"
msgstr "Nariši krepke vodoravne mrežne črte za sode ure"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to draw bolder/fatter horizontal grid lines for the even "
"hours (12am, 2am, 4am, etc)."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite narisati krepkejše/debelejše vodoravne mrežne "
"črte za sode ure (12:00, 14:00, 16:00 itd.)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show incidence descriptions in agenda view items"
msgstr "Pokaži opise incidence v točkah pogleda dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to display the incidence descriptions in agenda view items."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite prikazati opise incidence v elementih pogleda "
"dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show to-dos"
msgstr "Prikaži opravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This check box toggles the display of to-dos in the Day, Week and Month "
"views in the Agenda view. If you have too many to-dos which have a due date "
"associated, you may want to turn them off to avoid clutter."
msgstr ""
"To potrditveno polje preklopi prikaz opravil v pogledih dan, teden in mesec "
"v pogledu dnevnega reda. Če imate preveč opravil, ki imajo povezan rok, jih "
"boste morda želeli izklopiti, da se izognete neredu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show current-time (Marcus Bains) line"
msgstr "Pokaži vrstico trenutnega časa (Marcus Bains)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This check box toggles on or off a red line in the Day or Week view "
"indicating the current time (Marcus Bains line). This line gives you an "
"indication of how much time is left &eg; until a meeting takes place."
msgstr ""
"To potrditveno polje vklopi ali izklopi rdečo črto v pogledu dneva ali "
"tedna, ki označuje trenutni čas (črta Marcusa Bainsa). V tej vrstici je "
"prikazano, koliko časa je ostalo &eg; dokler ne pride do sestanka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show seconds and timezone on the current-time (Marcus Bains) line"
msgstr ""
"Prikaži sekunde in časovni pas v vrstici (Marcus Bains) trenutnega časa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This check box toggles on or off the seconds on the current-time line "
"(Marcus Bains line). Depending on your locale, the timezone may also be "
"shown."
msgstr ""
"To potrditveno polje vklopi ali izklopi sekunde na vrstici trenutnega časa "
"(vrstica Marcusa Bainsa). V odvisnosti od vaše lokalne nastavitve je lahko "
"prikazan tudi časovni pas."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time range selection in agenda view starts event editor"
msgstr ""
"Izbira časovnega obsega v pogledu dnevnega reda zažene urejevalnik dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to start the event editor automatically when you select a "
"time range in the daily and weekly view. To select a time range, drag the "
"mouse from the start time to the end time of the event you are about to plan."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite samodejno zagnati urejevalnik dogodkov, ko "
"izberete časovno obdobje v dnevnem in tedenskem pogledu. Če želite izbrati "
"časovni razpon, povlecite miško od začetnega do končnega časa dogodka, ki ga "
"nameravate načrtovati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2269 index.docbook:2335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Tag inside, calendar outside</guilabel> option if you "
"would like to draw calendar items in their associated tag's color, with the "
"item's border drawn in the color of its calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost <guilabel>Oznaka znotraj, koledar zunaj</guilabel>, če "
"želite narisati koledarske elemente v pripadajoči barvi oznake, z obrobo "
"elementa, narisano v barvi njegovega koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Calendar inside, tag outside</guilabel> option if you "
"would like to draw calendar items in their associated calendar color, with "
"the item's border drawn in the color of its tag."
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost <guilabel>Koledar znotraj, oznaka zunaj</guilabel>, če "
"želite narisati elemente koledarja v pripadajoči barvi koledarja, pri čemer "
"je obroba elementa narisana v barvi njegove oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Only tag</guilabel> option if you would like to draw "
"calendar items (both inside and border) in the color of their associated tag."
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost <guilabel>Samo oznaka</guilabel>, če želite narisati "
"elemente koledarja (znotraj in rob) v barvi njihove povezane oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Only calendar</guilabel> option if you would like to "
"draw calendar items (both inside and border) in the color of their calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost <guilabel>Samo koledar</guilabel>, če želite elemente "
"koledarja (tako znotraj kot obrobe) narisati v barvi njihovega koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please use the <link linkend=\"config-main-colors\">Colors and Fonts</link> "
"configuration page for setting these colors."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev teh barv uporabite konfiguracijsko stran <link linkend="
"\"config-main-colors\">Barve in pisave</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2291 index.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color busy days with a different background color"
msgstr "Obarvajte naporne dni z drugačno barvo ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want Agenda view's background to be filled with a "
"different color on days which have at least one all day event marked as busy."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da se ozadje pogleda dnevnega reda zapolni z "
"drugo barvo ob dnevih, ko je vsaj en celodnevni dogodek označen kot zaseden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please look in the Colors configuration area to select the Agenda view "
"background busy color of your choosing."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, poglejte v območje za konfiguracijo barv, da izberete barvo ozadja "
"zasedenega pogleda dnevnega reda po vaši izbiri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Calendar Display"
msgstr "Prikaz več koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select if all calendars should be merged into one Agenda view, each calendar "
"should be displayed in its own Agenda view or if each view should be "
"available via tabs. The side by side view can be customized with "
"<guimenuitem>Configure View</guimenuitem> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali naj bodo vsi koledarji združeni v en pogled dnevnega reda, ali "
"naj bo vsak koledar prikazan v svojem pogledu dnevnega reda ali naj bo vsak "
"pogled na voljo prek zavihkov. Vzporedni pogled lahko prilagodite z "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj pogled</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Month View tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Mesečni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"month-view\">Month view</link> options:"
msgstr "Možnosti <link linkend=\"month-view\">Mesečni pogled</link>:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display Options"
msgstr "Možnosti zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the first four check boxes to display the time, icons (reminder, "
"recursion &etc;), to-dos or journals in Month view."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite prva štiri potrditvena polja za prikaz časa, ikon (opomnik, "
"rekurzija &etc;), opravil ali dnevnikov v mesečnem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want Month view's background to be filled with a "
"different color on days which have at least one all day event marked as busy."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da je ozadje mesečnega pogleda zapolnjeno z "
"drugo barvo ob dnevih, ko je vsaj en celodnevni dogodek označen kot zaseden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please look in the Colors configuration area to select the Agenda/Month view "
"background busy color of your choosing."
msgstr ""
"Poglejte v konfiguracijsko območje Barve, da izberete barvo ozadja pogleda "
"Dnevni/Mesečni po vaši izbiri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the colors for the Month view as in <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"views-agenda\">Agenda view</link>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte barve za pogled meseca kot v <link linkend=\"config-main-"
"views-agenda\">pogledu dnevnega reda</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Todo View tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pogled Todo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"todo-view\">Todo view</link> options:"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"todo-view\">Ogled opravil</link> možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always display completed to-dos at the bottom of the list"
msgstr "Vedno prikaži dokončana opravila na dnu seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, all completed to-dos will be always grouped at "
"the bottom of the To-do List."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite to možnost, bodo vsa dokončana opravila vedno združena na dnu "
"seznama opravil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record completed to-dos in journal entries"
msgstr "Zabeležite dokončana opravila v vnose v dnevnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this box, &korganizer; will automatically add a journal entry "
"for every completed to-do."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to polje, &korganizer; samodejno doda vnos v dnevnik za vsako "
"opravljeno opravilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors and Fonts"
msgstr "Barve in pisave"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the color used for holidays, for highlighting, and for specific event "
"tags. You can choose a different color for each tag. Of course too many "
"colors may be confusing, so use common sense. The use of color depends also "
"on the <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">view preferences.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Izberite barvo, ki se uporablja za praznike, za poudarjanje in za posebne "
"oznake dogodkov. Za vsako oznako lahko izberete drugo barvo. Seveda lahko "
"preveč barv povzroči zmedo, zato uporabite zdrav razum. Uporaba barve je "
"odvisna tudi od <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">nastavitev pogleda.</"
"link>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Holiday color"
msgstr "Praznična barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the holiday color. The holiday color will be used for the holiday "
"name in the Month view and the holiday date in the Date Navigator."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete praznično barvo. Barva praznika bo uporabljena za ime "
"praznika v pogledu meseca in datum praznika v Krmarju po datumih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Agenda view background color"
msgstr "Barva ozadja pogleda dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the Agenda view background color."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo ozadja pogleda dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Busy days background color"
msgstr "Barva ozadja za obremenjene dni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the Agenda or Month view background busy color. This color is only "
"used when the option for drawing busy days with a different color is set in "
"either of these views."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo zasedenega ozadja dnevnega reda ali pogleda meseca. Ta "
"barva se uporablja le, če je v katerem koli od teh pogledov nastavljena "
"možnost za risanje dni z veliko prometa z drugo barvo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Agenda view current-time line color"
msgstr "Barva vrstice trenutnega časa pogleda dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select a color for the current-time (Marcus Bains) line."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo za vrstico trenutnega časa (Marcus Bains)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working hours color"
msgstr "Barva delovnega časa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the color of the working hours background in the Agenda view."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo ozadja delovnega časa v pogledu dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2415
#, no-c-format
msgid "To-do due today color"
msgstr "Opravila danes, barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the to-do due today color."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo opravila, ki je treba opraviti danes."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2421
#, no-c-format
msgid "To-do overdue color"
msgstr "Barva zapadlih opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the to-do overdue color."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberite barvo</guilabel>, v katerem "
"lahko izberete barvo zamujenega opravila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Month view today background color"
msgstr "Barva ozadja za današnji mesečni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button opens the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you "
"to select the background color for today's date in Month view."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, kjer lahko v "
"mesečnem pogledu izberete barvo ozadja za današnji datum."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group allows you to assign a color to each tag. Select a tag in the "
"drop down list, and press the button to open the <guilabel>Select Color</"
"guilabel> dialog, allowing you to select the color for that tag. <link "
"linkend=\"config-main-views\">Depending on the view preferences</link>, this "
"color will be used to mark events and to-dos which bear this tag in the "
"Agenda and Month views."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vam omogoča, da vsaki oznaki dodelite barvo. Na spustnem seznamu "
"izberite oznako in pritisnite gumb, da odprete pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>, v katerem lahko izberete barvo za to "
"oznako. <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">Odvisno od nastavitev pogleda</"
"link> bo ta barva uporabljena za označevanje dogodkov in opravil, ki nosijo "
"to oznako v pogledih Dnevni red in Meseci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Viri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group allows you to assign a color to each resource. Select a resource "
"in the drop down list, and press the button to open the <guilabel>Select "
"Color</guilabel> dialog, allowing you to select the color for that resource. "
"<link linkend=\"config-main-views\">Depending on the view preferences</"
"link>, this color will be used to mark events and to-dos which are stored "
"using this resource in the Agenda and Month views."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vam omogoča, da vsakemu viru dodelite barvo. Na spustnem seznamu "
"izberite vir in pritisnite gumb, da odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi "
"barvo</guilabel>, v katerem lahko izberete barvo za ta vir. <link linkend="
"\"config-main-views\">Odvisno od nastavitev pogleda</link> bo ta barva "
"uporabljena za označevanje dogodkov in opravil, ki so shranjeni s tem virom "
"v pogledih Dnevni red in Meseci."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pisave"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time bar"
msgstr "Časovna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to pick the font, font style and size for the time bar."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da izberete pisavo, slog pisave in velikost za časovno "
"vrstico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Month view"
msgstr "Mesečni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to pick the font, font style and size for the Month view."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da izberete pisavo, slog pisave in velikost za pogled "
"meseca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Agenda view"
msgstr "Pogled dnevnega reda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to pick the font, font style and size for the Agenda view "
"(Day, Week and Work Week views)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da izberete pisavo, slog pisave in velikost za pogled "
"Dnevni red (pogledi Dan, Teden in Delovni teden)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current-time (Marcus Bains) line"
msgstr "Vrstica trenutnega časa (Marcus Bains)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to pick the font, font style and size for the Marcus Bains "
"line (a colored line in the Agenda view indicating the current time)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da izberete pisavo, slog pisave in velikost za vrstico "
"Marcusa Bainsa (barvna črta v pogledu dnevnega reda, ki označuje trenutni "
"čas)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Groupware Communication"
msgstr "Uporabi skupinsko komunikacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to automatically send emails when creating, updating or "
"deleting events or to-dos which involve others. This email can be an "
"invitation to attendees of an event you created, a cancellation of an event "
"you created, an answer or an update on your invitation status, an event "
"change request, &etc; Check this option if you want to use the groupware "
"functionality (&eg; Configuring &kontact; as a &kde; <guilabel>Kolab</"
"guilabel> client)."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje za samodejno pošiljanje e-pošte pri ustvarjanju, "
"posodabljanju ali brisanju dogodkov ali opravil, ki vključujejo druge. To e-"
"poštno sporočilo je lahko povabilo udeležencem dogodka, ki ste ga ustvarili, "
"odpoved dogodka, ki ste ga ustvarili, odgovor ali posodobitev stanja vašega "
"povabila, zahteva za spremembo dogodka &etc; Označite to možnost, če želite "
"uporabljati funkcionalnost skupinske programske opreme (&eg;. Konfiguriranje "
"&kontact; kot odjemalca &kde; <guilabel>Kolab</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send copy to owner when mailing events"
msgstr "Pošlji kopijo lastniku pri pošiljanju dogodkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you check the <guilabel>Send copy to owner when mailing events</"
"guilabel> box, you will get a copy of all email messages that &korganizer; "
"sends at your request to the event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Ko označite polje <guilabel>Pošlji kopijo lastniku pri pošiljanju dogodkov</"
"guilabel>, boste prejeli kopijo vseh e-poštnih sporočil, ki jih &korganizer; "
"pošlje na vašo zahtevo udeležencem dogodka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mail transport"
msgstr "Prevoz pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose which type of mail transport you would like to use. You "
"can either use &kmail; or the &Sendmail; command (which must be installed on "
"your system in order to work)."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete vrsto prevoza pošte, ki jo želite uporabiti. Uporabite "
"lahko &kmail; ali &Sendmail; ukaz (ki mora biti nameščen v vašem sistemu, da "
"deluje)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish"
msgstr "Objavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By publishing your free/busy information, you allow others to take your busy "
"time schedule into account when inviting you to an event."
msgstr ""
"Z objavo podatkov o prostem/zasedenem drugem omogočite, da vaš urnik "
"upoštevajo, ko vas povabijo na dogodek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish free/busy information automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno objavi informacije o prostem/zasedenem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you wish your Free/Busy information to be uploaded "
"automatically. Note that you may skip this option and choose to mail or "
"upload your Free/Busy information via the <guilabel>Schedule</guilabel> menu "
"of &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite, da se vaši podatki o prostem/zasedenem "
"nalagajo samodejno. Upoštevajte, da lahko preskočite to možnost in izberete "
"pošiljanje ali nalaganje informacij o prostem/zasedenem prek menija "
"<guilabel>Urnik</guilabel> v &korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your application is setup to work as a <guilabel>&kde; Kolab client</"
"guilabel>, this is not required. The <guilabel>Kolab2</guilabel> server can "
"take care of publishing your Free/Busy information and manage the access to "
"it from other users."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaša aplikacija nastavljena za delo kot <guilabel>&kde; Odjemalec "
"Kolab</guilabel>, to ni potrebno. Strežnik <guilabel>Kolab2</guilabel> lahko "
"poskrbi za objavo vaših informacij o prosti/zasedenosti in upravlja dostop "
"drugih uporabnikov do njih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum time between uploads (in minutes)"
msgstr "Minimalni čas med nalaganji (v minutah)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to publish your information automatically, you can configure "
"the interval of time in minutes between each upload."
msgstr ""
"Če se odločite za samodejno objavo svojih podatkov, lahko konfigurirate "
"časovni interval v minutah med vsakim nalaganjem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish (default 60) days of free/busy information"
msgstr "Objavi (privzeto 60) dni informacij o prostem/zasedenem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the number of calendar days you wish to be published and available "
"to others"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte število koledarskih dni, za katere želite, da so objavljeni "
"in na voljo drugim"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2573 index.docbook:2638
#, no-c-format
msgid "Server &URL;"
msgstr "Strežnik &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the &URL; for the server on which your Free/Busy information will be "
"published. Ask the server administrator for this information."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite &URL; za strežnik, na katerem bodo objavljeni vaši podatki o prostem/"
"zasedenem stanju. Za te informacije vprašajte skrbnika strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kolab2 server example: <userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/freebusy/joe@kolab2."
"com.ifb</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Primer strežnika Kolab2: <userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/freebusy/joe@kolab2."
"com.ifb</userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2582 index.docbook:2647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username"
msgstr "Uporabniško ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the login information relative to your account on the server"
msgstr "Vnesite podatke za prijavo v zvezi z vašim računom na strežniku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kolab2 server specificity: your registered UID (Unique IDentifier), by "
"default, would be similar to your email address on the Kolab2 server but it "
"may be different. In this case enter your UID. Ask the server administrator "
"about your UID if you do not know it."
msgstr ""
"Specifičnost strežnika Kolab2: vaš registrirani UID (enolični IDentifier) bi "
"bil privzeto podoben vašemu e-poštnemu naslovu na strežniku Kolab2, vendar "
"je lahko drugačen. V tem primeru vnesite svoj UID. Vprašajte skrbnika "
"strežnika o svojem UID-ju, če ga ne poznate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2591 index.docbook:2654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password"
msgstr "Geslo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2592 index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter your password (server login password) here."
msgstr "Tukaj vnesite svoje geslo (geslo za prijavo v strežnik)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2596 index.docbook:2660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember password"
msgstr "Zapomni si geslo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want &korganizer; to remember your password and "
"skip asking you each time it uploads your Free/Busy information."
msgstr ""
"Označite to možnost, če želite &korganizer; da si zapomni vaše geslo in vas "
"ne sprašuje vsakič, ko naloži podatke o prosti/zasedenosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2600 index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not recommended to store your password in the configuration file for "
"security reasons."
msgstr ""
"Iz varnostnih razlogov ni priporočljivo shranjevati gesla v konfiguracijski "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2609
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieve"
msgstr "Pridobi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By retrieving other people's free/busy information, you can take their busy "
"time schedule into account when inviting them to an event."
msgstr ""
"Če pridobite informacije o prosti/zasedenosti drugih oseb, lahko upoštevate "
"njihov urnik zasedenosti, ko jih povabite na dogodek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieve other people's free/busy information automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno pridobi informacije o zasedenosti drugih oseb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automate the process for retrieving other users free/busy time. Fill in the "
"server information section below to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Avtomatizirajte postopek za pridobivanje časa prostih/zasedenih drugih "
"uporabnikov. Izpolnite spodnji razdelek s podatki o strežniku, da omogočite "
"to možnost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use full email address for retrieval"
msgstr "Uporabi polni e-poštni naslov za iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting lets you change the name of the file which will be fetched from "
"the server. If you check this option, it will download a free/busy file "
"called <userinput>user@domain.ifb</userinput>, else it will fetch "
"<userinput>user.ifb</userinput>. Ask the server administrator if you are not "
"sure about how to configure this option."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev vam omogoča, da spremenite ime datoteke, ki bo pridobljena s "
"strežnika. Če označite to možnost, bo prenesel datoteko o prostem/zasedenem "
"stanju, imenovano <userinput>user@domain.ifb</userinput>, sicer bo pridobil "
"<userinput>user.ifb</userinput>. Vprašajte skrbnika strežnika, če niste "
"prepričani, kako konfigurirati to možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Kolab2 server specificity:</guilabel> If you are configuring "
"&korganizer; as a component to a <guilabel>&kde; Kolab client (&kontact;/"
"Kolab)</guilabel> you have to check this option."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Posebnost strežnika Kolab2:</guilabel> Če konfigurirate "
"&korganizer; kot komponenta datoteke <guilabel>&kde; Odjemalec Kolab "
"(&kontact;/Kolab)</guilabel> to možnost morate označiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the &URL; for the server from which your Free/Busy information will be "
"fetched. Ask the server administrator for this information."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite &URL; za strežnik, s katerega bodo pridobljeni vaši podatki o "
"prostem/zasedenem stanju. Za te informacije vprašajte skrbnika strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Kolab2 server example: </guilabel><userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/"
"freebusy/</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Primer strežnika Kolab2: </guilabel><userinput>webdavs://kolab2."
"com/freebusy/</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the login information relative to your account on the server."
msgstr "Vnesite podatke za prijavo v zvezi z vašim računom na strežniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want &korganizer; to remember your password and "
"skip asking you each time it fetches the free/busy files."
msgstr ""
"Označite to možnost, če želite &korganizer; da si zapomni vaše geslo in vas "
"ne vpraša vsakič, ko pridobi datoteke o prostem/zasedenem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2673 index.docbook:2694
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about configuring plugins, please refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"plugins-chapter\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o konfiguraciji vtičnikov glejte <xref linkend=\"plugins-"
"chapter\"/>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Pages"
msgstr "Strani po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to add your own &GUI; Elements to store your own values "
"into &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran vam omogoča dodajanje lastnega &GUI; Elementi za shranjevanje "
"lastnih vrednosti v &korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create your elements as described in <guilabel>How does this work?</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite svoje elemente, kot je opisano v <guilabel>Kako to deluje?</"
"guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; provides you with the possibility of extending the application "
"with plugins."
msgstr "&korganizer; nudi možnost razširitve aplikacije z vtičniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugins can be configured under the &korganizer; main configuration "
"dialog. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Configure &korganizer;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click the "
"<guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> icon on the icon list sidebar of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnike je mogoče konfigurirati pod &korganizer; glavno konfiguracijsko "
"pogovorno okno. Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Konfiguriraj &korganizer;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"in kliknite ikono <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> v stranski vrstici seznama "
"ikon v pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Plugins"
msgstr "Razpoložljivi vtičniki"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date Numbers Plugin for Calendars"
msgstr "Vtičnik datumskih številk za koledarje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin adds the number of the day in the year to the Agenda view. For "
"instance, February 1 is day number 32."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik doda številko dneva v letu v pogled dnevnega reda. Na primer, 1. "
"februar je dan številka 32."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia 'This Day in History' Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik Wikipedia 'Ta dan v zgodovini'"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin provides links to Wikipedia's <quote>This Day in History</quote> "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik ponuja povezave do strani Wikipedije <quote>Ta dan v zgodovini</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia Picture of the Day Plugin for Calendars"
msgstr "Vtičnik Wikipedia Slika dneva za koledarje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid "This plugin provides the Wikipedia <quote>Picture of the Day</quote>."
msgstr "Ta vtičnik ponuja Wikipedijino <quote>Sliko dneva</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jewish Calendar Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik Judovski koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin provides Jewish calendar dates in addition to the Gregorian "
"calendar dates. In the configuration dialog of the plugin, you can choose if "
"you want to display Israeli holidays, weekly Parsha, day of Omer and/or Chol "
"HaMoed."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik ponuja datume judovskega koledarja poleg datumov gregorijanskega "
"koledarja. V konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu vtičnika lahko izberete, ali "
"želite prikazati izraelske praznike, tedensko paršo, dan Omerja in/ali Chol "
"HaMoeda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "Referenca"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2750
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Meniji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &korganizer; starts, the main &korganizer; window appears. The window "
"has several components: a menubar, a toolbar, a month calendar, a main panel "
"with the current <quote>view</quote> of events, and a to-do list."
msgstr ""
"Ko &korganizer; se začne glavni &korganizer; pojavi se okno. Okno ima več "
"komponent: menijsko vrstico, orodno vrstico, mesečni koledar, glavno ploščo "
"s trenutnim <quote>pogledom</quote> dogodkov in seznam opravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menus provide access to all the common operations that can be performed "
"with the calendar, including saving, loading, adding and deleting events, to-"
"dos and journal entries, printing and more."
msgstr ""
"Meniji omogočajo dostop do vseh običajnih operacij, ki jih je mogoče "
"izvajati s koledarjem, vključno s shranjevanjem, nalaganjem, dodajanjem in "
"brisanjem dogodkov, opravili in vnosi v dnevnik, tiskanjem in drugim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that when using &korganizer; as the calendar component of "
"&kontact;, the menus differ from the stand alone application."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da pri uporabi &korganizer; kot komponenta koledarja &kontact;, "
"se meniji razlikujejo od samostojne aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2765
#, no-c-format
msgid "File"
msgstr "Datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu provides access to functions involving the "
"entire calendar."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> omogoča dostop do funkcij, ki vključujejo "
"celoten koledar."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a file dialog allowing you to select a new vCalendar or "
"iCalendar file to load.</action> If you have made changes to the current "
"calendar, you will be given the option of saving them before loading a new "
"one."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno datoteke, v katerem lahko izberete novo "
"datoteko vCalendar ali iCalendar za nalaganje.</action> Če ste spremenili "
"trenutni koledar, boste imeli možnost, da jih shranite, preden naložite "
"novega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this, please refer to <xref linkend=\"managing-"
"import-export\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem glejte <xref linkend=\"managing-import-export\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> or click the <guilabel>Print</"
"guilabel> icon to <action>print the current calendar</action>. You can "
"specify the range of dates to be printed (either manually or with the "
"Calendar Widget) and the Print Style (Day, Week, Month or To-dos and "
"Journal)."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem> ali kliknite ikono "
"<guilabel>Natisni</guilabel>, da <action>natisnete trenutni koledar</"
"action>. Določite lahko obseg datumov za tiskanje (bodisi ročno ali s "
"pripomočkom za koledar) in slog tiskanja (dan, teden, mesec ali opravila in "
"dnevnik)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2809
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu> Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu> Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose <guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem> or click the "
"<guiicon>Print Preview</guiicon> icon, <action>the current calendar will be "
"printed on your screen, instead of on your printer</action>. Use this "
"feature to check if the printout will be correct before you start printing."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</guimenuitem> ali kliknete ikono "
"<guiicon>Predogled tiskanja</guiicon>, <action>bo trenutni koledar natisnjen "
"na vašem zaslonu, namesto na vašem tiskalniku</action>. S to funkcijo "
"preverite, ali bo izpis pravilen, preden začnete tiskati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify the range of dates to be printed (either manually or with "
"the Calendar Widget) and the View Type (Day, Week, Month or To-do)."
msgstr ""
"Določite lahko obseg datumov, ki jih želite natisniti (ročno ali s "
"pripomočkom za koledar) in vrsto pogleda (dan, teden, mesec ali opravilo)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Import "
"Calendar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Uvoz "
"koledar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a different iCalendar or vCalendar file somewhere, and you would "
"like to <action>merge its contents into your own calendar, add as a new "
"resource or open it as a new window</action>, choose this menu item. A good "
"time to do this would be if you received a vCalendar with a few entries via "
"email, for instance."
msgstr ""
"Če imate nekje drugo datoteko iCalendar ali vCalendar in bi želeli "
"<action>združiti njeno vsebino v svoj koledar, dodati kot nov vir ali jo "
"odpreti v novem oknu</action>, izberite ta menijski element. Pravi čas za to "
"bi bil, če bi na primer po e-pošti prejeli vCalendar z nekaj vnosi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-import\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"managing-import\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"as iCalendar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvozi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi kot iCalendar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action will export all your active events, to-dos and journal entries "
"(independent of to which resource they belong) as a new iCalendar file."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje bo izvozilo vse vaše aktivne dogodke, opravila in vnose v dnevnik "
"(ne glede na to, kateremu viru pripadajo) kot novo datoteko iCalendar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-export\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"managing-export\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Archive Old Incidences...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Arhiviraj stare primere ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2858
#, no-c-format
msgid "From time to time you should delete your old events."
msgstr "Od časa do časa bi morali izbrisati svoje stare dogodke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2860 index.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-purge-archive\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"managing-purge-archive"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Purge Completed To-dos</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Čiščenje dokončanih opravil</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action will remove all the completed to-dos from your active calendar."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje bo odstranilo vsa dokončana opravila iz vašega aktivnega "
"koledarja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> or click the <guiicon>Quit</"
"guiicon> icon, <action>the current calendar window will quit, prompting you "
"to save if the current calendar has been modified but not yet saved.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem> ali kliknete ikono "
"<guiicon>Zapri</guiicon>, <action>zapre trenutno okno koledarja in vas "
"pozove, da shranite, če je bil trenutni koledar spremenjen, vendar še ni "
"shranjen. </action>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has no effect on other calendar windows which may be opened. You have "
"to quit each calendar window individually."
msgstr ""
"To ne vpliva na druga okna koledarja, ki se lahko odprejo. Zapreti morate "
"vsako okno koledarja posebej."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Uredi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> menu you can edit and search events and "
"to-dos."
msgstr ""
"Z menijem <guilabel>Uredi</guilabel> lahko urejate in iščete dogodke in "
"opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>, and "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> menu items behave in the same fashion as in "
"other &kde; applications. With the <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem> menu item "
"you can find events and to-dos across the current calendar."
msgstr ""
"Menijski elementi <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</"
"guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> se obnašajo na enak način "
"kot v drugih &kde; aplikacije. Z menijsko postavko <guimenuitem>Najdi</"
"guimenuitem> lahko poiščete dogodke in opravila v trenutnem koledarju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undo the latest action</action>, or in other words, return the "
"calendar to the state it was immediately before the latest action."
msgstr ""
"<action>Razveljavi zadnje dejanje</action>, ali z drugimi besedami, vrnite "
"koledar v stanje, v katerem je bil neposredno pred zadnjim dejanjem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Redo the latest action</action>, or in other words, return the "
"calendar to the state it was immediately before the latest undo."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponovi zadnje dejanje</action>, ali z drugimi besedami, vrnite "
"koledar v stanje, v katerem je bil tik pred zadnjo razveljavitvijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cuts the currently selected event(s) to the clipboard, removing them from "
"your calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izreže trenutno izbrane dogodke v odložišče in jih odstrani iz koledarja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the currently selected item(s) to the clipboard, but leaving them "
"untouched."
msgstr ""
"Kopira trenutno izbrane elemente v odložišče, vendar jih pusti nedotaknjene."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> <action>inserts the contents of the "
"clipboard into your calendar</action>. The clipboard must contain a valid "
"vCalendar or iCalendar item, provided either by a previous Cut/Copy "
"operation or from a selection made outside of &korganizer;. You will be "
"warned if the contents of the clipboard cannot be understood."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> <action>vstavi vsebino odložišča v vaš "
"koledar</action>. Odložišče mora vsebovati veljaven element vCalendar ali "
"iCalendar, ki ga zagotovi predhodna operacija Izreži/Kopiraj ali izbor izven "
"&korganizer;ja. Če vsebine odložišča ni mogoče razumeti, boste opozorjeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, you can safely use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> hotkeys to copy text data from any outside application to a "
"&korganizer; Edit Event window and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Vendar pa lahko varno uporabite  <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> in tipkovne bližnjice <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> za kopiranje besedilnih podatkov iz "
"katere koli zunanje aplikacije v &korganizer; Okno Uredi dogodek in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2988
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the currently selected item(s), removing them from your calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izbrišite trenutno izbrane elemente in jih tako odstranite iz svojega "
"koledarja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> or "
"click the <guiicon>Find</guiicon> icon to <action>find events, to-dos and "
"journal entries according to their summary, description, and/or tags</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guimenuitem>Najdi</guimenuitem> v <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> ali "
"kliknite ikono <guiicon>Najdi</guiicon>, da <action>poiščete dogodke, "
"opravila in vnose v dnevnik glede na njihov povzetek, opis in/ali oznake</"
"action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"search-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"search-view\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3019
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Ogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several different <quote>views</quote> available for displaying "
"your events, to-dos and journal entries. &korganizer; is smart enough to "
"remember in between sessions what the last active view was, and the next "
"time it is started, it will display that view."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo je več različnih <quote>pogledov</quote> za prikaz vaših dogodkov, "
"opravil in vnosov v dnevnik. &korganizer; je dovolj pameten, da si med "
"sejami zapomni, kateri je bil zadnji aktivni pogled, in ob naslednjem zagonu "
"bo prikazal ta pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, each view will provide a way of displaying your journal entries, "
"to-dos and events, constrained to a particular time period or style of "
"display. Click any item to select it for further action. <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> click an item to bring up a menu with options such as "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>, and so "
"on. You can also use the <guimenu>Action</guimenu> menu to perform similar "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno bo vsak pogled nudil način prikaza vaših vnosov v dnevnik, "
"opravil in dogodkov, omejenih na določeno časovno obdobje ali slog prikaza. "
"Kliknite poljuben element, da ga izberete za nadaljnje dejanje. "
"<mousebutton>Desni gumb</mousebutton> kliknite element, da se prikaže meni z "
"možnostmi, kot so <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Izbriši</"
"guimenuitem> itd. Za izvajanje podobnih operacij lahko uporabite tudi meni "
"<guimenu>Dejanje</guimenu>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3038
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agenda</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dnevni red</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Agenda view."
msgstr "Preklop zaslona na pogled dnevnega reda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3044 index.docbook:3211 index.docbook:3224 index.docbook:3240
#: index.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"agenda-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"agenda-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3051
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Month View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mesečni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Month view."
msgstr "Preklopite zaslon na pogled meseca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"month-view\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"month-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3064
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Timeline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Časovnica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3068
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Timeline view."
msgstr "Preklopi zaslon na pogled časovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"timeline-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"timeline-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3078
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>To-do List</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seznam opravil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the To-do List view."
msgstr "Preklopite zaslon na pogled seznama opravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"todo-"
"view\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"todo-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Event List</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Seznam dogodkov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the list view."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz na pogled seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"list-"
"view\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"list-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> View</guimenu><guimenuitem>What's Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kaj je naslednje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the what's next view."
msgstr "Preklopi zaslon na pogled kaj je naslednje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view displays your next events and to-dos. Events and to-dos are "
"displayed one per line."
msgstr ""
"Ta pogled prikazuje vaše naslednje dogodke in opravila. Dogodki in opravila "
"so prikazani po eno na vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"whatsnext-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"whatsnext-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Journal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dnevnik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Journal view."
msgstr "Preklop zaslona na pogled dnevnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"journal-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"journal-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Osveži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updates or refreshes the currently displayed view."
msgstr "Posodobi ali osveži trenutno prikazani pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Povečava</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this submenu to adjust the current view to show more or less data."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ta podmeni, da prilagodite trenutni pogled za prikaz več ali manj "
"podatkov.Uporabite ta podmeni za prilagoditev trenutnega pogleda za prikaz "
"več ali manj podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the Agenda view (Day(s) or Week view), you can use the zoom actions to "
"show more or less days (<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>In Horizontally</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Out Horizontally</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>), or more or less hours in the day "
"(<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>In Vertically</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Out Vertically</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu dnevnega reda (pogled dneva(-ov) ali tedna) lahko uporabite "
"dejanja povečave, da prikažete več ali manj dni "
"(<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Povečava</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Vodoravno</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice > in <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Pomanjšaj</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj vodoravno</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) ali "
"več ali manj ur v dnevu (<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Povečaj</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem >Navpično</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Povečaj</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Navpično pomanjšaj</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu offers access to the filters already created using the <link "
"linkend=\"menu-settings-edit-filters\"><guilabel>Edit Calendar Filters</"
"guilabel></link> dialog. <action>Select on this submenu the filter that will "
"be used in &korganizer; view</action>. If you do not want to use a filter, "
"choose <guilabel>No filter</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni ponuja dostop do filtrov, ki so že ustvarjeni s pogovornim oknom "
"<link linkend=\"menu-settings-edit-filters\"><guilabel>Urejanje filtrov "
"koledarja</guilabel></link>. <action>V tem podmeniju izberite filter, ki bo "
"uporabljen v &korganizer; ogled</action>. Če ne želite uporabiti filtra, "
"izberite <guilabel>Brez filtra</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Go</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pojdi</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about browsing &korganizer; views, please refer to "
"<xref linkend=\"description-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o brskanju &korganizer; ogledov, glejte <xref linkend="
"\"description-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Backward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous day, week or month, depending on the view."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnji dan, teden ali mesec, odvisno od pogleda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3187
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next day, week, or month, depending on the view."
msgstr "Pojdite na naslednji dan, teden ali mesec, odvisno od pogleda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3197
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>To Today</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Na danes</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the period of time that includes the current day."
msgstr "Pojdite na časovno obdobje, ki vključuje trenutni dan."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Day</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dan</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Day view."
msgstr "Preklop zaslona na dnevni pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next x Days</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednjih x dni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Next x Day view, where x is defined in "
"&korganizer; main configuration."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite zaslon na pogled Naslednji x dan, kjer je x določen v "
"&korganizer; glavna konfiguracija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Work Week</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delovni teden</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Work Week view."
msgstr "Preklopite zaslon na pogled Delovni teden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the same as the Week view, except only the working days of the week "
"are shown."
msgstr ""
"To je enako kot tedenski pogled, le da so prikazani samo delovni dnevi v "
"tednu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Week</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teden</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Week view."
msgstr "Preklopite zaslon na tedenski pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Week view provides a view similar to the Day view. Events for seven days "
"are shown next to each other. All of the functions available for the Day "
"view are available in the Week view, too."
msgstr ""
"Tedenski pogled ponuja pogled, podoben dnevnemu pogledu. Dogodki za sedem "
"dni so prikazani drug poleg drugega. Vse funkcije, ki so na voljo za dnevni "
"pogled, so na voljo tudi v tedenskem pogledu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Event...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov dogodek...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>New Event...</guilabel> to <action>create a new event</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Nov dogodek ...</guilabel>, da <action>ustvarite nov "
"dogodek</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get a detailed description of the event window in <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-events\">the Entering Events</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podroben opis okna dogodkov lahko dobite v razdelku <link linkend=\"entering-"
"data-events\">Vnos dogodkov</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New To-do...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo opravilo ...</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo opravilo ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>New To-do...</guilabel> to <action>create a new to-do</"
"action>. Initially the to-do has no due date, but you can specify one."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Novo opravilo ...</guilabel>, da <action>ustvarite novo "
"opravilo</action>. Sprva opravilo nima roka, vendar ga lahko določite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get a detailed description of the to-do window in <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-to-do\">the Entering To-dos</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podroben opis okna opravil najdete v <link linkend=\"entering-data-to-do"
"\">razdelku Vnos opravil</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Sub-to-do...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo podopravilo ...</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo podopravilo ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>New Sub-to-do...</guilabel> to <action>start writing a new "
"sub-to-do. The currently selected to-do will be the sub-to-do parent</"
"action>. Initially the to-do has no due date, but you can specify one."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Novo pod-opravilo ...</guilabel>, da <action>začnete "
"pisati novo pod-opravilo. Trenutno izbrano opravilo bo nadrejeno "
"podopravilu</action>. Sprva opravilo nima roka, vendar ga lahko določite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get a detailed description of the to-do window in <link linkend="
"\"entering-data-to-do\">Entering To-dos</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podroben opis okna opravil najdete v razdelku <link linkend=\"entering-data-"
"to-do\">Vnos opravil</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Journal...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov dnevnik...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>New Journal...</guilabel> to <action>start writing a new "
"journal entry</action>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Nov dnevnik ...</guilabel>, da <action>začnete pisati nov "
"vnos v dnevnik</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3319
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pick a Date</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poberi datum</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a a date selection dialog for quickly navigating the view."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za izbiro datuma za hitro krmarjenje po pogledu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Show</guilabel> to <action>open a dialog showing the "
"details of the currently selected journal entry, event or to-do.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Pokaži</guilabel>, da <action>odprete pogovorno okno, ki "
"prikazuje podrobnosti trenutno izbranega vnosa v dnevnik, dogodka ali "
"opravila.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Edit...</guilabel> to <action>edit the currently selected "
"journal entry, event or to-do.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Uredi ...</guilabel> za <action>urejanje trenutno "
"izbranega vnosa v dnevnik, dogodka ali opravila.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> &Del; </shortcut> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> &Del; </shortcut> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Delete</guilabel> to <action>remove the currently selected "
"journal entry, event or to-do.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Izbriši</guilabel>, če želite <action>odstraniti trenutno "
"izbrani vnos v dnevnik, dogodek ali opravilo.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Make Sub-to-do Independent</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naredi podopravila neodvisna</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Make Sub-to-do Independent</guilabel> to detach the "
"currently selected sub-to-do item from its parent and make it an independent "
"to-do item."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Naredi podopravilo neodvisno</guilabel>, da trenutno "
"izbrani element podopravila ločite od njegovega nadrejenega in ga naredite "
"kot neodvisen element opravila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule"
msgstr "Razpored"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Publish Item Information...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Objavi informacije o artiklu ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Email the selected event, to-do or journal entry in the iCalendar format."
msgstr ""
"Po e-pošti pošljite izbrani dogodek, opravilo ali vnos v dnevnik v obliki "
"iCalendar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"publish\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"publish\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send Invitation to Attendees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji povabilo udeležencem</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send the selected to-do or event to the attendees, and, if necessary, "
"request a response from them."
msgstr ""
"Izbrano opravilo ali dogodek pošljite udeležencem in po potrebi od njih "
"zahtevajte odgovor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"request\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"request\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send Status Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji posodobitev stanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you changed your status as an attendee, choose this menu item to send "
"your updated status (accepted, tentative, &etc;) to the item's organizer."
msgstr ""
"Če ste spremenili svoj status kot udeleženec, izberite to postavko menija, "
"da pošljete svoje posodobljeno stanje (sprejeto, pogojno &etc;) "
"organizatorju predmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"reply"
"\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"reply\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send Cancellation to Attendees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji preklic udeležencem</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you plan to cancel an event or to-do, select it, and choose this menu "
"item to notify the attendees about the cancellation."
msgstr ""
"Če nameravate preklicati dogodek ali opravilo, ga izberite in izberite ta "
"element menija, da obvestite udeležence o preklicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"cancel\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"cancel\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3420
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Request Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zahtevaj posodobitev</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zahtevaj posodobitev</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request the latest version of the selected event or to-do from the organizer."
msgstr ""
"Od organizatorja zahtevajte najnovejšo različico izbranega dogodka ali "
"opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"refresh\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"refresh\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3431
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Request Change</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zahtevaj spremembo</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Razpored</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zahtevaj spremembo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send an alternative proposal to the organizer of the selected event or to-do."
msgstr ""
"Pošljite alternativni predlog organizatorju izbranega dogodka ali opravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"counter\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"counter\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mail Free Busy Information...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Informacije o prosti zasedenosti po "
"pošti ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email your Free Busy information to one or more email addresses."
msgstr ""
"Po e-pošti pošljite informacije o zasedenosti na enega ali več e-poštnih "
"naslovov.Po e-pošti pošljite podatke o zasedenosti na enega ali več e-"
"poštnih naslovov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3459 index.docbook:3470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"free-"
"busy\"/>."
msgstr "Za več informacij o tem dejanju glejte <xref linkend=\"free-busy\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Schedule</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upload Free Busy Information</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Urnik</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nalaganje informacij o prosti "
"zasedenosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Upload your Free Busy information to the groupware server. Other users will "
"then be able to retrieve the information."
msgstr ""
"Naložite informacije o prosti zasedenosti na strežnik skupinske programske "
"opreme. Drugi uporabniki bodo nato lahko pridobili informacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings and Help"
msgstr "Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; menus described in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals "
"documentation &korganizer; has these application specific Settings and Help "
"menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; meniji, opisani v poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Osnovna dokumentacija "
"&korganizer; ima te vnose menija Nastavitve in Pomoč, specifične za "
"aplikacijo:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3488
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sidebar</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Stranska vrstica</"
"guisubmenu><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Stranska vrstica</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Click the menu items of this submenu to show or hide &korganizer; "
"sidebar components</action>. Note that the sidebar is visible only when "
"<link linkend=\"config-main-views\">the current view does not use the full "
"window.</link>"
msgstr ""
"<action>Kliknite elemente menija v tem podmeniju, da prikažete ali skrijete "
"&korganizer; komponente stranske vrstice</action>. Upoštevajte, da je "
"stranska vrstica vidna le, če <link linkend=\"config-main-views\">trenutni "
"pogled ne uporablja celotnega okna.</link>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Date &amp; Time...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj datum &amp; Čas ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Click this menu item to set the desktop date and time formats</"
"action>. Note that this setting is shared between other desktop applications."
msgstr ""
"<action>Kliknite ta element menija, da nastavite oblike zapisa datuma in "
"časa namizja</action>. Upoštevajte, da si to nastavitev delijo druge namizne "
"aplikacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Manage View Filters...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Upravljanje filtrov pogleda ...</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Choose this menu item to open the <guilabel>Edit Filters</guilabel> "
"dialog</action>. Using this dialog, you can create, delete and edit filters "
"that will affect which items will be displayed by &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite ta element menija, da odprete pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Urejanje filtrov</guilabel></action>. V tem pogovornem oknu lahko "
"ustvarjate, brišete in urejate filtre, ki bodo vplivali na elemente, ki jih "
"bo prikazal &korganizer;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3520
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Tags...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje oznak ...</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje oznak ..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Choose this menu item to open the <guilabel>Manage Tags</guilabel> "
"dialog</action>. Using this dialog, you can create, delete and edit calendar "
"item tags. Tags are used to organize your events and to-dos in related "
"groups."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite ta element menija, da odprete pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Upravljanje oznak</guilabel></action>. V tem pogovornem oknu lahko "
"ustvarjate, brišete in urejate oznake koledarskih elementov. Oznake se "
"uporabljajo za organiziranje vaših dogodkov in opravil v povezanih skupinah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Druge funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter, you'll learn of other useful features of &korganizer;: what "
"tricks you can do with a click of your mouse."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju boste spoznali druge uporabne funkcije &korganizer;: kakšne "
"trike lahko naredite z enim klikom miške."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line"
msgstr "Ukazna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A nice program to access a &kde; calendar from the command line is "
"konsolekalendar."
msgstr ""
"Lep program za dostop do &kde; koledar iz ukazne vrstice je konsolekalendar."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop Operations"
msgstr "Operacije povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; can be easily controlled with your mouse. The supported drag-"
"and-drop operations are detailed below."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; lahko enostavno nadzorujete z miško. Podprte operacije povleci "
"in spusti so podrobno opisane spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any event can be re-sized with your mouse. Simply move the mouse pointer "
"near the top or bottom edge of the event, and drag the edge up or down. This "
"way you can visually modify the starting and ending time of your "
"appointment. This works in the Day, Week and Work Week views."
msgstr ""
"Vsakemu dogodku lahko spremenite velikost z miško. Preprosto premaknite "
"kazalec miške blizu zgornjega ali spodnjega roba dogodka in povlecite rob "
"navzgor ali navzdol. Tako lahko vizualno spremenite začetni in končni čas "
"vašega termina. To deluje v pogledih Dan, Teden in Delovni teden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any event can be rescheduled with your mouse. Move the mouse pointer over "
"the event, and drag it to a new time location. This works in the Day, Week "
"and Work Week views."
msgstr ""
"Vsak dogodek lahko prestavite z miško. Premaknite kazalec miške nad dogodek "
"in ga povlecite na novo časovno lokacijo. To deluje v pogledih Dan, Teden in "
"Delovni teden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Events can be copied to other, presently non-visible dates. Move the mouse "
"pointer over the event, and drag it to the Date Navigator on the left side "
"of the current calendar, or to the Date Navigator of a different calendar."
msgstr ""
"Dogodke lahko kopirate na druge, trenutno nevidne datume. Kazalec miške "
"premaknite nad dogodek in ga povlecite v Krmar po datumih na levi strani "
"trenutnega koledarja ali v Krmar po datumih drugega koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, you cannot drag from Agenda view in one calendar to Agenda view in "
"another calendar."
msgstr ""
"Vendar ne morete povleči iz pogleda dnevnega reda v enem koledarju v pogled "
"dnevnega reda v drugem koledarju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toolbars can be dragged on the screen. Move the mouse pointer over the "
"toolbar's handle, and drag it to a new location on your screen."
msgstr ""
"Orodne vrstice lahko povlečete po zaslonu. Premaknite kazalec miške nad "
"ročaj orodne vrstice in ga povlecite na novo mesto na zaslonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use freebusy-time with &korganizer;?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabim prosti čas z &korganizer;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, follow the instructions in <link linkend=\"config-main-free-busy\">Free/"
"Busy</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da, sledite navodilom v <link linkend=\"config-main-free-busy\">Prost/"
"zaseden</link>."

